ys%20been%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Cheng%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20when%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20eventually%20expanded%20our%20family%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20San%20Francisco%20or%20the%20Bay%20Area%20in%20general%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20we%20both%20earn%20good%20salaries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdinks-buy-homes-parents-spend-most-income-on-mortgage-childcare-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708484455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d528f0a3bd891424f8c1a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdinks-buy-homes-parents-spend-most-income-on-mortgage-childcare-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20seems%20like%20only%20couples%20with%20two%20incomes%20and%20no%20kids%20can%20afford%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20right%20now%20in%20many%20of%20America's%20priciest%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22alloyd%40insider.com%20(Alcynna%20Lloyd)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdinks-buy-homes-parents-spend-most-income-on-mortgage-childcare-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%3A%20Is%20a%20Political%20Conspiracy%20at%20Play%20in%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20MLA%20Manoj%20Manzil's%20Life%20Imprisonment%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20174624%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-20-at-5.45.54-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%20(Bihar)%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20conviction%2C%20life%20sentence%20and%20subsequent%20assembly%20disqualification%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20leader%20Manoj%20Manzil%20is%20making%20headlines%2C%20as%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20case%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzil%2C%20first%20time%20MLA%20and%20firebrand%20Dalit%20leader%20of%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20in%20a%20nine-year-old%20murder%20case%20and%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20on%20February%2013.%20With%20his%20conviction%2C%20he%20was%20disqualified%20from%20the%20membership%20of%20the%20state%20legislative%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Manzil%2C%2022%20other%20people%20aged%20between%2025%20and%2090%20years%2C%20also%20assumed%20to%20be%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20workers%2C%20have%20been%20found%20guilty%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Jay%20Prakash%20Singh%20and%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20Bhojpur%20district%E2%80%99s%20MP%2FMLA%20court%20wrote%20in%20its%2023-page%20judgment%2C%20%E2%80%9CProsecution%20has%20failed%20to%20bring%20any%20peculiar%20fact%20that%20would%20place%20the%20acts%20of%20the%20convicts%20in%20the%20rarest%20of%20rare%20category%20to%20merit%20the%20sentence%20of%20death.%20So%20the%20court%20cannot%20award%20the%20convicts%20the%20benefit%20of%20Probation%20of%20Offenders%20Act%20and%20will%20award%20substantive%20sentences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%2023%20accused%20were%20awarded%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20for%20life%20and%20Rs%2010%2C000%20fine%20under%20section%20302%2F149%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20ten%20years%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20and%20Rs%2010%2C000%20fine%20under%20section%20364%2F149%20of%20IPC%20and%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20imprisonment%20and%20Rs%205%2C000%20fine%20under%20section%20201%2F149%20of%20IPC%2C%20according%20to%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20order%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20sentences%20awarded%20are%20to%20run%20concurrently%20and%20the%20period%20of%20detention%2C%20if%20any%2C%20undergone%20by%20the%20convicts%2C%20during%20the%20investigation%2C%20inquiry%20of%20trial%20shall%20be%20set%20off%20as%20per%20the%20provision%20laid%20down%20under%20section%20428%20of%20the%20CrPC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20has%20termed%20the%20judgment%20a%20%E2%80%9Cjudicial%20massacre%E2%80%9D%20and%20alleged%20that%20Manzil%20and%20the%20others%20were%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvictim%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20hatched%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20feudal%20forces%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Bhojpur%2C%20these%20forces%20have%20been%20continuously%20trying%20to%20stop%20the%20movement%20of%20Dalits%20and%20the%20poor%20by%20sending%20our%20leaders%20to%20jail%20or%20creating%20massacres%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kunal%2C%20Bihar%20state%20secretary%20of%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20massacres%20of%20Dalits%20and%20the%20poor%20took%20place%20in%20the%20same%20Bhojpur%20district%20but%20culprits%20have%20not%20been%20punished%20till%20date%20even%20in%20one%20case.%20A%20grave%20injustice%20has%20been%20done%20to%20our%20leaders%20who%20became%20the%20voice%20of%20Dalits%20and%20the%20poor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20the%20persons%20sentenced%20belong%20to%20poor%2C%20Dalit%20and%20the%20OBC%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20could%20be%20a%20bigger%20judicial%20massacre%20than%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kunal%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%20of%20Jay%20Prakash%E2%80%99s%20murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20of%20Jay%20Prakash%20was%20believed%20to%20be%20due%20to%20a%20fallout%20over%20the%20murder%20of%20Satish%20Yadav%2C%20a%20local%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20leader%2C%20who%20was%20murdered%20on%20August%2020%2C%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20evening%2C%20Jay%20Prakash%20and%20his%20son%20Chandan%20Kumar%20Singh%20were%20returning%20to%20their%20village%20after%20buying%20vegetables%20from%20Badgaon%20market%20when%20the%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20was%20holding%20a%20meeting%20in%20this%20market%20against%20the%20murder%20of%20Satish%20Yadav.%20Manzil%20was%20allegedly%20present%20in%20this%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20when%20Jay%20Prakash%20and%20his%20son%20neared%20Nariyadih%2C%20Manzil%20and%20others%20started%20assaulting%20them%20with%20sticks%2C%20bricks%20and%20stones.%20Chandan%20fled%20from%20the%20site%20but%20Jay%20Prakash%20didn%E2%80%99t%20return%20to%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2027%2C%202015%20Chandan%20was%20informed%20by%20the%20police%20that%20Jay%20Prakash%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20found%20from%20a%20nearby%20canal.%20Chandan%20identified%20the%20body%20and%20the%20body%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20him%20after%20post-mortem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post-mortem%20report%20concluded%20that%20strangulation%20led%20to%20cardio-respiratory%20failure%20which%20caused%20death.%20A%20local%20court%20took%20cognisance%20of%20the%20case%20on%20March%2015%2C%202019%20and%20after%20three%20years%2C%20charges%20were%20framed%20and%20trial%20initiated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20in%20the%20case%20included%20nine%20eyewitnesses%2C%20including%20the%20deceased%20person%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20doctor%20who%20conducted%20post-mortem%20and%20an%20investigating%20officer%2C%20post-mortem%20report%20and%20chargesheet%20but%20no%20material%20evidence%20was%20produced.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20defence%20could%20not%20produce%20oral%2C%20documentary%20and%20material%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20murder%20of%20Satish%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatish%20Yadav%20entered%20politics%20at%20the%20age%20of%2020.%20His%20father%20was%20a%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20leader%20and%20had%20unsuccessfully%20fought%20assembly%20elections%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20tickets.%20Following%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20path%2C%20Satish%20also%20joined%20the%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20in%201995.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSatish%20had%20taken%20up%20the%20fight%20against%20the%20Ranveer%20Sena%20and%20fought%20several%20historic%20battles%20as%20part%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20propaganda%20squad.%20His%20capabilities%20soon%20made%20him%20a%20popular%20leader%20within%20the%20party%20as%20well%20as%20with%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20wrote%20about%20Satish%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpiml.org%2Fml-update%2Fvol-18-no-35%2Fcomrade-satish-yadav-a-life-sketch%2F%5C%22%3Eobituary%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20paddy%20crop%20was%20ready%2C%20he%20led%20a%20historic%20struggle%20for%20its%20purchase%20in%20Agiaon%20and%20forced%20the%20administration%20to%20purchase%2030%2C000%20quintals%20of%20paddy%20from%20sharecroppers%20and%20small%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20party%20added%20in%20the%20obituary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2020%2C%202015%2C%20Satish%20Yadav%20was%20returning%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Kamaria%20village%20after%20addressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Badgaon.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20he%20was%20attacked%20by%20armed%20assailants.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20government%20hospital%20where%20doctors%20declared%20him%20dead.%20Four%20persons%20were%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20including%20Rinku%20Singh%20and%20Awadhesh%20Sah.%20Jay%20Prakash%20was%20a%20close%20relative%20of%20Rinku%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRinku%20Singh%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Badgaon%20panchayat%20PACS%20(Primary%20Agricultural%20Credit%20Societies)%2C%20was%20also%20pressured%20by%20comrade%20Satish%20to%20purchase%20paddy%20from%20farmers.%20Even%20now%2C%20he%20owes%20Rs%208%20lakhs%20to%20the%20farmers%20as%20purchase%20arrears%2C%20for%20which%20comrade%20Satish%20was%20incessantly%20fighting%2C%E2%80%9D%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinku%20Singh%20is%20currently%20Karni%20Sena%E2%80%99s%20state%20president.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20he%20is%20associated%20with%20BJP%20MP%20R.K.%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinku%20Singh%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20any%20link%20with%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20link%20with%20Ranveer%20Sena%20or%20BJP.%20I%20am%20associated%20with%20Karni%20Sena.%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20Rinku%20Singh%20had%20an%20enmity%20with%20Manzil.%20In%20September%202021%2C%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jagran.com%2Fbihar%2Fpatna-city-karani-sena-state-president-rinku-singh-blamed-cpi-ml-mla-manoj-manjil-for-involvement-in-barmeshwar-mukhia-murder-case-21986829.html%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Manzil%20may%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Ranveer%20Sena%20(an%20upper%20caste%20militant%20group)%20chief%20Brahmeshwar%20Mukhiya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Satish%20Yadav%20murder%20case%2C%20two%20persons%20including%20Rinku%20Singh%20were%20acquitted%20in%202019%20and%20two%20persons%20are%20still%20absconding.%20Although%20Rinku%20Singh%20claimed%20he%20has%20no%20enmity%20with%20Manoj%20Manzil%2C%20he%20asserted%20that%20he%20was%20framed%20in%20the%20Satish%20Yadav%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20panchayat%20elections%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20candidates%20often%20get%20defeated%20and%20we%20win%20that%20is%20why%20they%20are%20angry%20with%20us%20and%20are%20framing%20us%20in%20fake%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rinku%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Manoj%20Manzil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhojpur%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Naxalbari%E2%80%99%20of%20Bihar%2C%20has%20been%20the%20stronghold%20of%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20as%20the%20first%20Naxalbari%20kind%20of%20armed%20movement%20against%20feudal%20castes%20in%20Bihar%20started%20from%20this%20district%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9980s.%20There%20is%20a%20great%20influence%20of%20the%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20among%20Dalits%20of%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201984%20to%20an%20agricultural%20labourer%20family%20in%20Kapurdihra%20village%20under%20Tarari%20police%20station%20in%20Bhojpur%20district%2C%20Manzil%20belongs%20to%20the%20Chamar%20caste%20which%20falls%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzil%20is%20a%20born%20rebel%20and%20has%20been%20an%20activist%20since%20his%20school%20days.%20When%20he%20was%20in%20the%20ninth%20standard%2C%20along%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20Manzil%20protested%20for%20basic%20amenities%20in%20Bhojpur%E2%80%99s%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20Awasiya%20Vidyalaya%20where%20he%20was%20studying.%20The%20school%20authority%20had%20issued%20transfer%20certificates%20against%20them%20for%20protesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzil%20is%20hugely%20inspired%20by%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20leader%20Ram%20Naresh%20Ram%20who%20died%20in%202010%20at%20the%20age%20of%2084.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%2C%20Ram%20Naresh%20Ram%20the%20was%20first%20line%20%E2%80%98revolutionary%E2%80%99%20who%20took%20arms%20against%20feudal%20forces.%20Manzil%20keeps%20a%20picture%20of%20Ram%20Naresh%20Ram%20along%20with%20student%20leader%20Chandrashekhar%20in%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20known%20Manzil%20for%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20since%20he%20was%20studying%20in%20Ambedkar%20Hostel%20in%20Arrah%C2%A0%20town%20and%20was%20preparing%20for%20civil%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20Kumar%20Bunti%2C%20a%20CPI-ML%C2%A0%20(Liberation)%20leader%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20visited%20Ambedkar%20hostel.%20He%20came%20to%20us%20and%20we%20talked%20for%20several%20hours.%20He%20had%20a%20longing%20for%20the%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20movement.%20He%20had%20curiosities%20regarding%20the%20Dalit%20leadership%20and%20movement%20of%20the%20country.%20He%20is%20fond%20of%20comrade%20Ram%20Naresh%20Ram%20and%20he%20would%20say%20that%20today%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20become%20such%20a%20leader%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20Kumar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20omnipresent%20influence%20of%20the%20revolutionary%20movement%20of%20Bhojpur%2C%20the%20leadership%20of%20Ram%20Naresh%20Ram%20and%20the%20increasing%20activities%20of%20AISA%20%E2%80%93%20student%20wing%20of%20CPI-ML%C2%A0%20(Liberation)%20%E2%80%93%20made%20him%20a%20man%20of%20the%20movement.%20Many%20movements%20for%20hostel%20reform%20took%20place%20under%20his%20leadership.%20He%20led%20many%20struggles%20of%20the%20students.%20He%20became%20the%20national%20president%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Youth%20Association.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20his%20fighting%20spirit%20and%20art%20of%20strengthening%20the%20movement%2C%20he%20reached%20important%20positions%20in%20the%20party%20and%20in%20the%202015%20Bihar%20assembly%20elections%2C%20he%20was%20given%20a%20ticket%20from%20the%20Agiaon%20assembly%20seat%20which%20was%20carved%20out%20in%202008%20delimitation.%20The%20seat%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20stronghold%20of%20the%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20as%20well%20as%20Ranveer%20Sena.%20He%20had%20contested%20this%20election%20while%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20he%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20again%20gave%20him%20a%20ticket%20from%20Agiaon.%20This%20time%20again%20he%20was%20arrested%20%2C%20but%20got%20bail%20a%20few%20days%20before%20voting.%20He%20won%20the%20election%20and%20reached%20the%20assembly%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20In%20this%20election%2C%20he%20defeated%20his%20nearest%20rival%20JDU%20leader%20Prabhunath%20Prasad%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2048%2C550%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20becoming%20an%20MLA%2C%20he%20used%20to%20lead%20public%20movements%20on%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20year%202019%2C%20a%2070-year-old%20school%20located%20near%20Koilwar%20bridge%20in%20Bhojpur%20was%20demolished%20for%20a%20four-lane%20road%20construction.%20Around%201%2C600%20students%20were%20studying%20in%20this%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20this%20school%2C%20Manzil%20went%20to%20every%20student%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20convinced%20their%20parents%20to%20protest.%20After%20the%20protests%2C%20the%20local%20government%20gave%20assurance%20that%20land%20will%20be%20allotted%20to%20build%20the%20school%20at%20another%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20after%20he%20became%20an%20MLA%2C%20Manzil%20again%20started%20the%20agitation%20for%20this%20institute%20which%20later%20became%20a%20movement%20for%20schools%20in%20general.%20On%20September%201%2C%202021%2C%20he%20started%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESadak%20par%20School%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(school%20on%20the%20road)%20movement%20and%20on%20this%20movement%E2%80%99s%20launch%20day%2C%20Manzil%20ran%20the%20school%20located%20near%20Koilwar%20bridge%20for%2011%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20%E2%80%98Sadak%20par%20School%E2%80%99%20campaign%C2%A0%20he%20started%20teaching%20children%20on%20the%20road%20where%20there%20were%20no%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Satyadev%20Kumar%2C%20member%20of%20Arrah%20Town%20Committee%20of%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20Covid%20in%202021%2C%20when%20there%20was%20an%20outcry%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20people%20were%20confined%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhaskar.com%2Flocal%2Fbihar%2Fnews%2Fbihar-communist-party-mla-manoj-manzil-care-coronavirus-patients-during-second-wave-128731264.html%3F_branch_match_id%3D1240539144538438879%26utm_campaign%3D128731264%26utm_medium%3Dsharing%26_branch_referrer%3DH4sIAAAAAAAAA8soKSkottLXT0nMzMvM1k3Sy8zTL3fJDiiLKq0yz0gCAKGsaDwfAAAA%5C%22%3EManzil%20used%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20Sadar%20hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20located%20in%20Arrah%20throughout%20the%20day%20to%20ensure%20that%20patients%20received%20the%20necessary%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSadar%20Hospital%20falls%20in%20Arrah%20assembly%20constituency%2C%20whose%20MLA%20is%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20in%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20Covid-19%2C%20he%20was%20not%20seen%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20but%20Manoj%20Manzil%20remained%20in%20the%20hospital%20continuously%20and%20helped%20in%20getting%20treatment.%20Today%20the%20blood%20bank%20in%20Sadar%20Hospital%20remains%20open%2024X7%2C%20the%20credit%20for%20this%20goes%20to%20Manzil%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhojpur-based%20journalist%20Prashant%20Kumar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManzil%20kept%20struggling%20on%20the%20streets%20even%20after%20becoming%20an%20MLA.%20For%20him%20the%20road%20and%20assembly%20were%20one.%20Interestingly%2C%20his%20movement%20was%20not%20limited%20to%20his%20own%20assembly%20constituency.%20He%20used%20to%20hold%20protests%20in%20other%20assembly%20constituencies%20also%20on%20grassroots%20issues.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20obvious%20that%20the%20MLAs%20of%20those%20assembly%20constituencies%20are%20jealous%20of%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20journalist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20verdict%2C%20when%20he%20was%20being%20taken%20to%20police%20custody%2C%20Manzil%20said%20that%20he%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20conspiracy%20and%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20Dalit%20and%20downtrodden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20to%20move%20high%20court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20against%20the%20district%20court%20order.%20Kunal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20against%20this%20verdict.%20We%20are%20discussing%20it%20with%20our%20Patna%20lawyers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKameshwar%20Singh%2C%20the%20lawyer%20who%20represented%20Manzil%2C%20believes%20that%20there%20are%20many%20shortcomings%20in%20the%20verdict%20and%20it%20will%20not%20stand%20in%20the%20Patna%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dead%20body%20was%20recovered%20after%20nine%20days%20of%20the%20missing%20complaint%20and%20in%20a%20completely%20decomposed%20state.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20anyone%20to%20identify%20the%20body%20but%20J.P.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20son%20identified%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kameshwar%20Singh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20DNA%20report%20of%20the%20deceased%20is%20yet%20to%20come%2C%20but%20the%20court%20pronounced%20the%20verdict.%20The%20body%20was%20scientifically%20not%20proven%20to%20be%20of%20J.P.%20Singh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20mentioned%20that%20the%20doctor%20who%20conducted%20the%20post-mortem%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20deceased%20person%E2%80%99s%20age%20seemed%2040%20years%2C%20but%20his%20son%20informed%20that%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20age%20was%2055%20years.%20Notably%2C%20Chandan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20age%20is%2045%20years.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20the%20deceased%20had%20a%20son%20when%20he%20was%20just%2010%20years%20old.%20Is%20it%20possible%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kameshwar%20Singh%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20lacunae%20in%20this%20case.%20We%20are%20confident%20that%20the%20high%20court%20will%20deliver%20justice%20in%20our%20favour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708484091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20174624%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-20-at-5.45.54-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-is-a-political-conspiracy-at-play-in-cpi-ml-liberation-mla-manoj-manzils-life-imprisonment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20has%20termed%20the%20judgment%20as%20%E2%80%98judicial%20massacre%E2%80%99%20and%20alleged%20that%20Manzil%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20hatched%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20feudal%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-is-a-political-conspiracy-at-play-in-cpi-ml-liberation-mla-manoj-manzils-life-imprisonment%22%2C%22