meet-ms-dhoni-after-the-international-game%2Farticleshow%2F107866557.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20wicketkeeper%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20is%20eagerly%20anticipating%20an%20interaction%20with%20former%20India%20skipper%20MS%20Dhoni%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Test%20match%20between%20India%20and%20England%20in%20Ranchi.%20Jurel%20shared%20a%20video%20by%20the%20BCCI%20expressing%20admiration%20for%20Dhoni%2C%20reminiscing%20about%20their%20first%20encounter%20during%20IPL%202021.%20Jurel's%20dream%20is%20to%20meet%20Dhoni%2C%20especially%20after%20an%20international%20game%2C%20after%20the%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fengland-in-india%2Findian-wicketkeeper-batter-dhruv-jurel-expresses-anticipation-to-meet-ms-dhoni-after-the-international-game%2Farticleshow%2F107866557.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Hacker%20Who%20Conned%20US%20Woman%20Of%20Rs%201.23%20Crore%20Jailed%20For%204%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2024-year-old%20Indian%20man%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%2051%20months%20in%20prison%20by%20a%20US%20court%20for%20defrauding%20an%20elderly%20American%20woman%20out%20of%20%24150%2C000%C2%A0(Rs%201%2C24%2C33642)%20through%20a%20computer%20hacking%20scheme%2C%20according%20to%20a%20US%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defendant%2C%20identified%20as%20Sukhdev%20Vaid%20from%20Haryana%2C%20India%2C%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20wire%20fraud%20charges%20in%20December%202023.%20Prosecutors%20allege%20he%20participated%20in%20a%20wider%20scheme%20targeting%20elderly%20Americans%20nationwide%2C%20resulting%20in%20over%20%241.2%20million%20in%20total%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2014th%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-mt%2Fpr%2Findia-based-computer-hacking-scam-targeted-elderly-across-country-and-stole-150000%5C%22%3Ecourt%20further%20ordered%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20upon%20release%20from%20custody%2C%20Vaid%20would%20be%20remanded%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Customs%20and%20Immigration%20Enforcement%20for%20deportation%20and%20ordered%20Vaid%20to%20pay%20%241%2C236%2C470%20(Rs%2010%2C24%2C92172)%20in%20restitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20all%20too%20common%20for%20people%20outside%20of%20our%20country%20to%20victimize%20Montanans%2C%20especially%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20wire%20fraud%2C%20and%20get%20away%20with%20it.%20But%20not%20this%20time.%20Vaid%20is%20going%20to%20federal%20prison%20due%20to%20the%20sophistication%20and%20tenacity%20of%20the%20FBI%2C%20for%20which%20I%20am%20grateful.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20relentless%20in%20tracking%20down%20these%20criminals%20who%20prey%20on%20our%20trusting%20impulses%2C%20and%20we%20are%20confident%20such%20efforts%20will%20result%20in%20these%20fraudsters%20ending%20up%20in%20the%20same%20place%20as%20Vaid%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Attorney%20Laslovich%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Phantom%20Hacker'%20scams%20layer%20imposter%20tech%20support%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20government%20personas%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20someone's%20computer%20and%20personal%20information.%20Sadly%2C%20these%20scams%20are%20increasingly%20targeting%20our%20seniors.%20Adding%20to%20the%20depravity%20of%20this%20particular%20case%20is%20that%20the%20scammer%20traveled%20overseas%20to%20collect%20the%20victim's%20money%20in%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Special%20Agent%20in%20Charge%20Shohini%20Sinha%20of%20the%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20FBI.%20%26quot%3BTo%20protect%20yourself%2C%20never%20click%20on%20unsolicited%20pop-ups%20or%20links%20sent%20by%20text%20message%20or%20email%2C%20don't%20download%20software%20at%20the%20request%20of%20someone%20you%20don't%20know%2C%20and%20always%20remember%20that%20the%20government%20and%20law%20enforcement%20will%20never%20call%20and%20ask%20you%20for%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20court%2C%20the%20Montana%20victim%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20very%20violated...I%20have%20crawled%20into%20a%20shell%20emotionally%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20vulnerable%20in%20any%20way.%20I%20don't%20know%20who%20I%20can%20safely%20trust%20now.%20I%20don't%20feel%20safe%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20alleged%20in%20court%20documents%20that%20a%20large%20enterprise%20originating%20from%20India%20was%20involved%20in%20stealing%20%241%2C236%2C470%20from%20elderly%20Americans.%20The%20Montana%20case%20arose%20in%20February%202023%2C%20when%20Glacier%20Bank%20notified%20the%20FBI%20that%20Jane%20Doe%2C%20a%2073-year-old%20woman%20in%20Kalispell%2C%20had%20been%20defrauded.%20The%20fraudsters%20tricked%20Jane%20Doe%20into%20giving%20them%20money%20through%20a%20pop-up%20notice%20that%20appeared%20on%20Jane%20Doe's%20computer%20screen.%20The%20notice%20explained%20that%20Jane%20Doe%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bhacked%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20her%20to%20call%20a%20number%20for%20customer%20support.%20Jane%20Doe%20complied%2C%20and%20fraudsters%20directed%20her%20to%20remove%20cash%20from%20her%20bank%20accounts%20for%20safekeeping%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BFed.%26quot%3B%20Jane%20Doe%20complied%20and%20gave%20%24150%2C000%20in%20cash%20to%20the%20fraudsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20learning%20of%20the%20scam%2C%20the%20FBI%20set%20up%20a%20ruse%20in%20which%20Jane%20Doe%20told%20the%20fraudsters%20she%20still%20had%20%2450%2C000%20in%20cash.%20The%20FBI%20arrested%20Vaid%2C%20along%20with%20his%20co-defendant%2C%20Eddly%20Joseph%2C%20of%20Gainesville%2C%20Florida%2C%20when%20they%20traveled%20to%20Montana%20to%20collect%20the%20money.%20The%20investigation%20determined%20that%20the%20fraudsters%20remotely%20accessed%20Jane%20Doe's%20computer%2C%20using%20UltraViewer%2C%20which%20they%20installed%20on%20her%20computer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoseph%20was%20sentenced%20previously%20to%20two%20years%20and%20nine%20months%20in%20prison%20for%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708483380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fcyber-crime-generic-istock_650x400_81504427706.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-hacker-who-conned-us-woman-of-rs-1-23-crore-jailed-for-4-years-5097613%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20alleged%20in%20court%20documents%20that%20a%20large%20enterprise%20originating%20from%20India%20was%20involved%20in%20stealing%20%241%2C236%2C470%20from%20elderly%20Americans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-hacker-who-conned-us-woman-of-rs-1-23-crore-jailed-for-4-years-5097613%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-hacker-who-conned-us-woman-of-rs-1-23-crore-jailed-for-4-years-5097613%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-hacker-who-conned-us-woman-of-rs-1-23-crore-jailed-for-4-years-5097613%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Post%20Stokes'%20Criticism%2C%20England%20Great's%20Video%20Schooling%20Kohli%20On%20DRS%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20India%20vs%20England%20Test%2C%20which%20the%20hosts%20won%20by%20a%20huge%20margin%2C%20had%20its%20moments.%20From%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sarfaraz%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64385-sarfaraz-naushad-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E's%20debut%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E's%20commanding%20double%20ton%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-rav