autam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20Ranji%20Trophy%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20I%20had%20with%20Gambhir%20that%20day%20is%20the%20only%20regret%20I%20have%20because%20people%20who%20know%20me%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20I%20am%20not%20that%20sort%20of%20a%20person%20who%20goes%20out%20there%20and%20quarrels%20with%20seniors.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20those%20memories%20that%20I%20could%20have%20avoided.%20I%20have%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20my%20seniors%2C%20but%20due%20to%20one%20incident%2C%20it%20spoilt%20my%20image%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiwary%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fmy-biggest-regret-is-the-fight-with-gautam-gambhir-still-cant-believe-he-threatened-me-manoj-tiwary-after-retirement-article-107829700%5C%22%3ESports%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20and%20Tiwary%20rubbed%20shoulders%20with%20each%20other%20during%20their%20time%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20franchise%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%20The%20Bengal%20cricketer%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20quite%20close%20with%20the%20Delhi%20lad%20at%20one%20point%20but%20they%20eventually%20went%20their%20separate%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20I%20said%20it%20is%20my%20biggest%20regret%20because%20we%20were%20very%20close%20at%20one%20point%20in%20time.%20While%20playing%20for%20KKR%2C%20we%20used%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20discussions%20and%20brainstorm%20over%20who%20to%20pick%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20relationship%20was%20such%20that%20we%20used%20to%20go%20into%20details%20and%20inputs.%20But%20things%20did%20not%20pan%20out%20the%20way%20that%20it%20should%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20rued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwary%20also%20revealed%20that%20Gambhir%20once%20asked%20him%20to%20meet%20outside%20(to%20settle%20an%20argument)%20but%20it%20never%20happened.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTu%20bahar%20mil%20match%20ke%20baad%2C%20((Meet%20me%20after%20the%20match)%20a