r-dune-2-set-110-degrees-heat-stroke-1235917582%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korean%20Pastor%20Hailed%20As%20Hero%2C%20Jailed%20For%20Molesting%20Teen%20Refugees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20South%20Korean%20pastor%20once%20hailed%20as%20a%20hero%20for%20helping%20North%20Korean%20defectors%20escape%20to%20safety%20has%20been%20jailed%20for%20sexually%20abusing%20minors%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChun%20Ki-won%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20five%20years%20in%20prison%20last%20week%20for%20molesting%20six%20teenage%20victims%20between%202016%20and%202023%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20either%20North%20Korean%20refugees%20or%20children%20of%20refugees%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Seoul%20Central%20District%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nature%20of%20the%20crime%20was%20bad%20considering%20the%20circumstances%2C%20method%2C%20content%2C%20period%2C%20and%20number%20of%20crimes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20added%20that%20Chun%20had%20molested%20the%20teenagers%20while%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20position%20where%20he%20has%20absolute%20influence%20over%20the%20victims%20as%20a%20school%20principal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChun's%20crime%20appears%20to%20have%20had%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20victims'%20formation%20of%20sound%20sexual%20values%2C%20and%20the%20victims%20also%20wanted%20him%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChun%20was%20head%20of%20the%20Christian%20aid%20organization%20Durihana%2C%20which%20he%20claimed%20had%20helped%20more%20than%201%2C000%20defectors%20reach%20Seoul%20since%201999.%20According%20to%20the%20organization's%20website%2C%20it%20runs%20a%20boarding%20school%20for%20North%20Korean%20children%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Btaught%20the%20Christian%20faith.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChun%20was%20arrested%20and%20indicted%20last%20September%20for%20violating%20the%20Act%20on%20Sexual%20Protection%20of%20Children