20of%20two%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20would%20be%20%2433%2C524.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20program%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20last%20for%2018%20months%2C%20is%20primarily%20funded%20by%20money%20St.%20Louis%20received%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stlouis-mo.gov%2Fgovernment%2Fdepartments%2Fmayor%2Finitiatives%2Fgbi.cfm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Rescue%20Plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Twitter%20cofounder%20Jack%20Dorsey's%20%23startsmall%20philanthropic%20initiative%20also%20contributed%2C%20allowing%20the%20program%20to%20take%20on%20an%20extra%20100%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELayne%20said%20the%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20program%20took%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20planning%20and%20coordinating%20with%20partners%2C%20including%20researchers%20at%20Washington%20University%20in%20St.%20Louis.%20He%20said%20they%20are%20committed%20to%20gathering%20quantitative%20and%20qualitative%20data%20to%20measure%20the%20success%20of%20the%20program%20and%20that%20an%20in-depth%20progress%20report%20is%20planned%20for%20the%20halfway%20point%20of%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminneapolis-guaranteed-basic-income-program-results-study-gbi-ubi-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeasuring%20the%20program's%20success%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20tracking%20what%20recipients%20are%20spending%20money%20on%20and%20the%20immediate%20impacts%20it's%20having%20on%20their%20lives.%20That%20could%20mean%20if%20a%20person%20is%20able%20to%20go%20from%20having%20two%20jobs%20to%20one%20job%20and%20spend%20the%20extra%20time%20providing%20academic%20support%20to%20their%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20that%20could%20mean%20the%20recipients%20are%20in%20a%20more%20stable%20place%20financially%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%2018%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20see%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20for%20people%20who%20are%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20to%20get%20to%20a%20place%20of%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20Layne%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20from%20that%20place%20of%20stability%2C%20they%20can%20actually%20make%20better%20decisions%2C%20and%20decisions%20that%20are%20going%20to%20impact%20them%20long-term.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20track%20recipients%20well%20after%20their%20participation%20in%20the%20program%20to%20measure%20the%20long-lasting%20impacts.%20For%20instance%2C%20recipients%20may%20be%20able%20to%20raise%20their%20credit%20score%2C%20something%20that%2010%20years%20down%20the%20line%20could%20make%20them%20more%20likely%20to%20become%20homeowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Layne%2C%20a%20large%20measure%20of%20the%20program's%20success%20will%20simply%20be%20if%20they%20can%20continue%20it%20beyond%20this%20initial%20pilot%20program%20and%20do%20another%20cohort%20of%20recipients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20get%20people%20to%20a%20place%20of%20thriving%20rather%20than%20surviving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20the%20success%20of%20the%20program%20is%20critical%20to%20be%20able%20to%20show%20the%20data%20about%20what%20impact%20is%20this%20actually%20having%20on%20St.%20Louisans%2C%20and%20then%20how%20that%20impact%20then%20translates%20into%2C%20honestly%2C%20better%20options%20for%20the%20city.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-louis-guaranteed-basic-income-500-monthly-spent-bills-debt-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708480746000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d543eba610a9069d5ac518%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-louis-guaranteed-basic-income-500-monthly-spent-bills-debt-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22St.%20Louis%20Treasurer%20Adam%20Layne%20said%20participants%20in%20the%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20pilot%20program%20are%20spending%20the%20%24500%20a%20month%20to%20pay%20off%20bills%20and%20debt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fst-louis-guaranteed-basic-income-500-monthly-spent-bills-debt-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sandeshkhali%20Will%20Be%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20%26quot%3BDownfall%26quot%3B%3A%20Himanta%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20yesterday%20expressed%20grave%20concern%20over%20the%20situation%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20asserted%20that%20Sandeshkhali%20would%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bdownfall%26quot%3B%20of%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20criticised%20the%20treatment%20of%20journalists%20in%20Bengal%2C%20stating%20that%20those%20attempting%20to%20disclose%20the%20true%20state%20of%20affairs%20are%20being%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20violence%20by%20Trinamool%20leaders%20and%20multiple%20accounts%20of%20women%20alleging%20harassment%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20%2C%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20condition%20of%20Bengal%20is%20very%20bad%2C%20the%20journalists%20there%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20show%20the%20reality%20are%20also%20being%20arrested.%20The%20incident%20that%20happened%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20one%20cannot%20even%20imagine%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20law%20would%20take%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20atrocity%20on%20women.%20It%20was%20all%20in%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20State%20government.%20A%20syndicate%20was%20going%20on%20there.%20This%20has%20come%20out%20before%20the%20country.%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20law%20will%20take%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20further%20warned%20that%20a%20government%20perpetrating%20such%20atrocities%20would%20not%20remain%20in%20power%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrinamool%20may%20try%20all%20it%20wants%20but%20people%20won't%20remain%20silent.%20A%20government%20which%20commits%20atrocities%20like%20this%20will%20not%20last%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Monday%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20arrested%20a%20journalist%20associated%20with%20Republic%20TV%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(DGP)%20directing%20him%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20within%20two%20weeks%20in%20a%20case%20where%20a%20journalist%20of%20a%20vernacular%20news%20channel%20was%20unlawfully%20detained%20by%20police%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%2C%20who%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20wife%20of%20the%20journalist%20concerned%2C%20alleged%20that%20she%20has%20no%20access%20to%20him%20and%20is%20concerned%20about%20his%20well-being%2C%20the%20NHRC%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20further%20submitted%20that%20it%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20throttle%20the%20media%20in%20West%20Bengal%20through%20'coercion%20and%20intimidation'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20journalist%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sandeshkhali%20area%20has%20been%20witnessing%20unrest%20for%20over%2010%20days%20as%20women%20protestors%20are%20seeking%20justice%20against%20alleged%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20TMC%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20had%20accused%20Trinamool%20Congress%20strongman%20Shajahan%20Sheikh%20and%20his%20supporters%20of%20%26quot%3Bland-grab%20and%20sexually%20assa