3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20second%20Grand%20Alliance%20was%20formed%20in%20July%202022%2C%20RJD%20had%20offered%20Mr%20Kumar%20the%20option%20of%20outside%20support%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20he%20said%20it%20would%20not%20be%20right.%20Lalu-ji%20had%20gone%20to%20meet%20him%20before%20the%20election.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20give%20outside%20support%2C%20you%20keep%20running%20the%20government'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20they%20had%20any%20inkling%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20intention%20to%20ditch%20the%20Grand%20Alliance%20a%20second%20time%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20been%20dragging%20his%20feet%20on%20several%20work-related%20issues%2C%20which%20seemed%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20then%2C%20the%20alliance%20backed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20are%20on%20anyone's%20side%2C%20we%20stand%20strong.%20We%20had%20no%20problem%20with%20anything.%20We%20had%20even%20gone%20and%20told%20him%20that%20he%20could%20continue%20the%20government%2C%20we%20would%20provide%20outside%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20of%20the%20differences%20during%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Grand%20Alliance%201%20and%202%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%20even%20in%202015%2C%20they%20were%20not%20eager%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20he%20had%20changed%20sides%20several%20times%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20time%2C%20there%20was%20pressure%20from%20various%20leaders%20of%20the%20country.%20Operation%20Lotus%20was%20happening%20in%20some%20states.%20Nitish-ji%20said%20his%20party%20was%20also%20being%20split.%20There%20was%20pressure%20from%20all%20sides.%20So%20we%20thought%20since%20the%20real%20fight%20is%20in%202024%2C%20anti-BJP%20forces%20might%20as%20well%20get%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20where%20the%20alliance%20unravelled%2C%20he%20said%20the%20reason%20was%20Mr%20Kumar's%20inability%20to%20accept%20%26quot%3Bground%20realities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20declared%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bstuck%20in%202005%20and%202010%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Brefused%20to%20recognise%20that%20his%20time%20is%20over%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20downfall%20started%20in%202011-2012%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20Mr%20Kumar%20blamed%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party's%20Chirag%20Paswan%20for%20the%20poor%20performance%20of%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20United.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20party%20had%20slipped%20to%20the%20second%20spot%20in%20the%20last%20state%20election%2C%20falling%20far%20behind%20the%20BJP.%20Mr%20Paswan%2C%20who%20contested%20solo%20and%20was%20said%20to%20have%20split%20the%20pro-NDA%20votes%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20reason%20why%20many%20JD(U)%20candidates%20had%20failed%20to%20win%20at%20the%20hustings.%20The%20whole%20of%20it%20was%20attributed%20to%20a%20BJP%20conspiracy%20by%20many%20leaders%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20NDA%20formed%20government%20again%2C%20it%20did%20not%20last%20long.%20The%20alliance%20collapsed%20in%202022%2C%20with%20JD(U)%20allegations%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20split%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20stint%20with%20the%20second%20Grand%20alliance%20was%20shorter.%20Last%20month%2C%20he%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20for%20a%20record%20ninth%20time%2C%20forming%20a%20new%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20he%20had%20dumped%20less%20than%2018%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%20affairs%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20right%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Grand%20Alliance%2C%20he%20had%20said.%20Sources%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20been%20upset%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20in%20INDIA%20bloc's