quot%3B%20claimed%20Mr%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDindor%20said%20more%20than%2065%2C000%20smart%20classrooms%20have%20been%20built%20by%20the%20state%20government%20so%20far%20and%20another%2043%2C000%20are%20under%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Mission%20Schools%20of%20Excellence%20project%2C%20we%20have%20constructed%2015%2C000%20classrooms%20in%202023-24%20while%20construction%20for%20another%2015%2C000%20classrooms%20is%20under%20progress.%20More%20than%205%2C000%20computer%20labs%20have%20been%20constructed%20and%20work%20is%20on%20for%20creating%2015%2C000%20more%20such%20labs%20in%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20the%20dropout%20ratio%20in%20primary%20schools%20fell%20from%2037.22%20per%20cent%20to%202.68%20per%20cent%20in%202022-23%20due%20to%20the%20efforts%20undertaken%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20quality%20education%20in%20schools%2C%20a%20total%20of%2022%2C349%20Vidya%20Sahayak%20and%20Gyan%20Sahayak%20(contractual%20teachers)%20have%20been%20appointed%20in%20the%20year%202023-24.%20For%20the%20year%202024-25%2C%20more%20than%20Rs%202%2C785%20crore%20has%20been%20allocated%20for%20the%20upgradation%20of%20primary%20schools%20under%20the%20Mission%20Schools%20of%20Excellence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708469880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Ftu6udi0o_school-generic-classroom-generic-unsplash-650_625x300_13_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fover-300-state-run-schools-functioning-with-single-classroom-gujarat-assembly-5096946%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20total%20of%20341%20state-run%20primary%20schools%20in%20Gujarat%20functioned%20with