er%20once%20again.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20PPP%20co-chairman%20Asif%20Zardari%2C%2068%2C%20is%20slated%20to%20become%20the%20country's%20President%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PPP%20and%20PML-N%20have%20achieved%20the%20required%20number%2C%20and%20%5Bnow%5D%20we%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilawal%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party-backed%20candidates%20and%20Sunni%20Ittehad%20Council%20(SIC)%20failed%20to%20achieve%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20Parliament%20to%20form%20government%20in%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilawal%20hoped%20that%20the%20news%20of%20the%20political%20alliance%20with%20the%20PML-N%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20positive%20market%20response%20as%20the%20cash-strapped%20country%20faced%20a%20hung%20Parliament%20after%20the%20February%208%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20candidates%20-%20a%20majority%20backed%20by%2071-year-old%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%20--%20won%2093%20National%20Assembly%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20asserted%20that%20his%20PML-N%20now%20has%20the%20%26quot%3Brequired%20numbers%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20PPP%20to%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government%20as%20he%20thanked%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20for%20the%20positive%20conclusion%20to%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20prime%20minister%20emphasised%20the%20unity%20between%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20noting%20that%20they%20were%20well-positioned%20to%20form%20the%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20The%20Express%20Tribune%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PML-N%20won%2075%20seats%20while%20the%20PPP%20came%20third%20with%2054%20seats.%20The%20Muttahida%20Qaumi%20Movement%20Pakistan%20(MQM-P)%20has%20also%20agreed%20to%20support%20them%20with%20their%2017%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20form%20a%20government%2C%20a%20party%20must%20win%20133%20out%20of%20265%20contested%20seats%20in%20the%20266-member%20National%20Assembly%20or%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%2071-year-old%20Khan's%20PTI%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20newly%20cemented%20PPP%2C%20PML-N%20alliance%20as%20'PDM%202.0'%20%26quot%3BPDM%202.0%20%3D%20%23MandateThieves.%26quot%3B%20The%20announcement%20of%20the%20alliance%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20ended%20inconclusively%20on%20Monday%20as%20both%20sides%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20a%20power-sharing%20formula%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20was%20prime%20minister%20from%202022%20to%202023%2C%20said%20that%20the%20journey%20ahead%20for%20the%20new%20government%20would%20not%20be%20easy%20but%20fraught%20with%20many%20difficulties%20and%20obstacles.%20He%20asserted%20that%20the%20coalition%20alliance%20will%20tackle%20them%20together%2C%20the%20Dawn%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPPP%20co-chairperson%20Zardari%2C%20who%20was%20president%20from%202008%20to%202013%2C%20has%20said%20the%20struggle%20of%20the%20political%20alliance%20bidding%20to%20make%20the%20next%20government%20is%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20country%20and%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20February%208%20general%20elections%20have%20been%20controversial%2C%20with%20several%20serious%20allegations%20of%20widespread%20rigging%20to%20alter%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan's%20sister%20Aleema%20Khan%20said%20the%20PTI%20chief%20has%20termed%20the%20February%208%20elections%20%26quot%3Bmother%20of%20all%20rigging%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAleema%20met%20Imran%20Khan%20at%20Adiala%20Jail%20on%20Tuesday.%20She%20told%20repor