g%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17202229%2FForest-in-Odisha.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKochi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20States%20and%20Union%20territories%20must%20uphold%20the%20definition%20of%20forests%20as%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%201996%20judgment%20until%20they%20provide%20details%20of%20all%20recorded%20forests%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20said%20in%20an%20interim%20order%20on%20Monday%20(February%2019)%20while%20hearing%20several%20petitions%20contesting%20the%202023%20amendment%20to%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%20(FCA)%20of%201980.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20in%201996%20(popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGodavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment)%2C%20any%20area%20that%20meets%20the%20dictionary%20meaning%20of%20a%20forest%20should%20be%20considered%20a%20forest%20and%20protected%20under%20the%20FCA%20of%201980%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20it%20is%20not%20officially%20recorded%20as%20a%20forest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20amendment%20of%20the%20Act%20last%20year%20would%20change%20this%20and%20open%20up%20vast%20tracts%20of%20forest%20land%20(including%20deemed%20forests%20and%20community%20forests%2C%20which%20are%20not%20officially%20recorded%20as%20forests)%20to%20human%20activities%2C%20experts%20had%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20amendment%20became%20law%20in%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20last%20resort%2C%20several%20groups%20and%20organisations%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20October%202023%20against%20the%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20interim%20order%20in%20response%20to%20these%20petitions%2C%20it%20not%20only%20upheld%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20forest%20as%20specified%20in%20its%201996%20judgment%2C%20but%20also%20clarified%20that%20forest%20land%20cannot%20be%20diverted%20for%20safaris%20or%20zoos%20without%20the%20prior%20approval%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConservationists%20called%20the%20interim%20order%20a%20%E2%80%9Clandmark%E2%80%9D%20judgment%20that%20upholds%20the%20constitution%20and%20the%20principles%20of%20democracy%2C%20transparency%20and%20accountability%3B%20one%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20wildlife%20and%20ecosystems%20are%20%E2%80%9Cheaving%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDictionary%20meaning%20of%20forest%20holds%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FCA%20of%201980%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20legislations%20that%20provides%20for%20the%20conservation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20forests%20in%20several%20ways%2C%20including%20by%20restricting%20the%20use%20of%20forests%20for%20non-forest%20purposes%20(such%20as%20construction%20for%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20tourism).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20March%20last%20year%2C%20however%2C%20Union%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20introduced%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F164.100.47.4%2FBillsTexts%2FLSBillTexts%2FAsintroduced%2F80_2023_LS_ENG329202330923PM.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EForest%20(Conservation)%20Amendment%20Bill%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20worried%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20from%20scientists%20and%20conservationists%20to%20activists%20and%20retired%20forest%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20group%20of%20retired%20civil%20servants%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20October%20last%20year%20arguing%20that%20the%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202023%20dilutes%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20forest%20%E2%80%93%20as%20already%20defined%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20its%20judgment%20passed%20on%20December%2012%2C%201996%20(in%20the%20case%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ET.N.%20Godavarman%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGodavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment%2C%20as%20this%20popular%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20is%20known%2C%20land%20that%20satisfies%20the%20dictionary%20meaning%20of%20what%20a%20forest%20is%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20it%20is%20not%20officially%20recorded%20as%20a%20forest%20%E2%80%93%20is%20eligible%20for%20protection%20under%20the%20FCA%20of%201980.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20as%20per%20the%202023%20amendment%2C%20the%20new%20Act%20will%20apply%20only%20to%20lands%20notified%20as%20a%20forest%20under%20the%20Indian%20Forest%20Act%2C%201927%2C%20or%20those%20that%20have%20been%20officially%20recorded%20as%20a%20forest%20on%20or%20after%20October%2025%2C%201980.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20restriction%20of%20the%20definition%20of%20forests%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20would%20make%20it%20easy%20for%20the%20Aravalli%20hills%20(which%20are%20deemed%20forests)%20in%20Haryana%20to%20be%20diverted%20for%20tourism%20purposes%2C%20activists%20had%20argued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20already%20has%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20announced%20its%20plans%20to%20convert%20a%20tract%20of%20the%20Aravallis%20in%20the%20state%20into%20a%20safari%20project%20%E2%80%93%20to%2C%20ironically%2C%20compensate%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20primary%20forest%20that%20will%20be%20logged%20for%20the%20international%20container%20trans-shipment%20terminal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fglobal-development%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F07%2Findia-port-airport-power-plant-military-project-great-nicobar-island-death-sentence-shompen-indigenous-people-warning%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecoming%20up%20in%20the%20Great%20Nicobar%20Island%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDictionary%20meaning%20of%20forest%20holds%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20despite%20these%20serious%20concerns%20raised%20by%20experts%2C%20the%20Act%20became%20law%20%E2%80%93%20now%20called%20the%20Van%20(Sanrakshan%20Evam%20Samvardhan)%20Adhiniyam%2C%201980%20%E2%80%93%20after%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20passed%20it%2C%20and%20after%20it%20received%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20assent%20on%20August%204%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20no%20other%20alternatives%20in%20sight%2C%20several%20groups%20and%20organisations%20filed%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20amendment%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20a%20group%20of%20retired%20civil%20servants%20filed%20a%20petition%20arguing%20several%20points%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20amendment%20dilutes%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20forest%20as%20already%20defined%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGodavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20petition%20also%20said%20that%20as%20per%20Rule%2016%20of%20the%20Van%20(Sanrakshan%20Evam%20Samvardhan)%20Rules%2C%202023%2C%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20should%20prepare%20a%20consolidated%20record%20of%20forest%20lands%20within%20one%20year%20from%20the%20notification%20of%20the%202023%20amendment.%20This%20has%20not%20been%20done%20yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20this%20(and%20other%20similar%20petitions%20submitted%20by%20NGOs%20Vanashakti%20and%20the%20Goa%20Foundation)%20on%20February%2019%20as%20per%20legal%20news%20website%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fstatesuts-must-follow-definition-of-forest-given-by-godavarman-judgment-till-forests-are-identified-as-per-2023-rules-supreme-court-249897%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20passed%20an%20interim%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20ordered%20that%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20must%20uphold%20the%20definition%20of%20forests%20as%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGodavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment%20until%20they%20provide%20details%20of%20all%20recorded%20forests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGodavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment%20had%20also%20held%20that%20states%20form%20state%20expert%20committees%20(SECs)%20and%20develop%20reports%20that%20quantify%20and%20identify%20forest%20lands%20in%20each%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20none%20of%20these%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20all%20states%20have%20these%20committees%20or%20that%20the%20committees%20have%20submitted%20their%20reports%20either%2C%20Prakriti%20Srivastava%2C%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fconstitutionality-of-forest-conservation-act-2023-challenged-in-sc-centre-to-respond-in-6-weeks%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPending%20the%20completion%20of%20exercise%20by%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20state%20governments%20and%20Union%20territories%2C%20under%20Rule%2016%2C%20the%20principles%20which%20are%20elucidated%20in%20the%20judgment%20of%20this%20court%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ET.N.%20Godavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20must%20be%20continued%20to%20be%20observed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20interim%20order%20read%2C%20as%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fstatesuts-must-follow-definition-of-forest-given-by-godavarman-judgment-till-forests-are-identified-as-per-2023-rules-supreme-court-249897%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20Rule%2016%20includes%20within%20its%20ambit%20forest-like%20areas%20to%20be%20identified%20by%20the%20expert%20committee%2C%20unclassed%20forest%20lands%20and%20community%20forest%20lands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20interregnum%20therefore%2C%20while%20being%20guided%20by%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20statute%20and%20those%20contained%20in%20Rule%2016%2C%20the%20State%20Governments%20and%20UT%20administrations%20shall%20peremptorily%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20the%20ambit%20of%20expression%20%E2%80%9Cforest%E2%80%9D%20as%20explained%20in%20the%20decision%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ET.N.%20Godavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20interim%20order%20also%20added%20that%20any%20proposal%20to%20establish%20zoos%20or%20safaris%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20not%20be%20finally%20approved%20save%20and%20except%20with%20the%20prior%20permission%20of%20this%20court%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CLandmark%20forest%20judgment%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEnvironmentalist%20and%20activist%20Prerna%20Singh%20Bindra%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%20against%20the%20amendment%20%E2%80%93%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20landmark%20forest%20judgment%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20protected%20India%E2%80%99s%20forests%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20unprecedented%20diversion%20and%20destruction%E2%80%9D%20by%20upholding%20the%20dictionary%20meaning%20of%20forests%20as%20per%20the%201996%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGodavarman%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20importantly%2C%20it%20upholds%20our%20constitution%20and%20the%20democratic%20principles%20of%20democracy%2C%20transparency%20and%20accountability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20order%20holds%20the%20%5BUnion%20environment%20ministry%5D%20accountable%3A%20to%20place%20the%20SEC%20reports%20as%20well%20the%20geo-referenced%20forests%20as%20per%20the%20Lafarge%20order%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Surely%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20citizens%20deserve%20to%20know%20where%20our%20forests%20are%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSignificantly%2C%20the%20ministry%20had%20assured%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%20%E2%80%93%20no%20less%20%E2%80%93%20forests%20would%20be%20protected%20as%20per%20the%20SEC%20reports%3B%20while%20their%20veracity%20is%20unknown%2C%20even%20apparently%20to%20the%20ministry%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20commented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMP%20and%20former%20Union%20environment%20minister%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20this%20was%20yet%20another%20instance%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stopping%20%E2%80%9Canother%20set%20of%20blatantly%20illegal%20and%20disastrous%20Modi%20government%20schemes%E2%80%9D%2C%20after%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20social%20media%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20amendment%20to%20the%20FCA%20%E2%80%9Cstripped%20protections%20from%20%5Btwo%5D%20lakh%20square%20km%20of%20forest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20in%20complete%20violation%20of%20a%201996%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20%5Bsic%5D.%20This%20amendment%20would%20have%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20divert%20%E2%80%9Cdeemed%20forests%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20forests%20in%20the%20North%20East%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1759851972537233593%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eposted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20party%20applauds%20this%20order%2C%20and%20commits%20to%20protecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20forests%20and%20environment%20when%20we%20form%20an%20INDIA%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20leader%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20wildlife%20and%20the%20ecosystem%20of%20the%20highly%20degraded%20Aravallis%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Haryana%20are%20heaving%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20with%20the%20interim%20order%20from%20the%20honourable%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Neelam%20Ahluwalia%2C%20a%20forest%20campaigner%20working%20to%20protect%20the%20Aravallis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMaking%20a%20zoo%20and%20keeping%20animals%20in%20enclosures%20in%20wilderness%20spaces%20like%20the%20Aravalli%20range%20goes%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20the%20people%20in%20power%20start%20viewing%20our%20hills%20and%20forests%20for%20the%20critical%20ecosystem%20services%20they%20provide%20and%20leave%20them%20alone%20instead%20of%20viewing%20them%20and%20exploiting%20them%20as%20resources%20to%20mine%2C%20to%20build%20real%20waste%20on%2C%20to%20make%20zoos%20to%20earn%20money%20from%20tourism%2C%20to%20create%20landfills%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708452303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17202229%2F