%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107860725.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20was%20opposed%20to%20sending%20nuclear%20weapons%20to%20space%2C%20dismissing%20US%20accusations%20that%20Moscow%20was%20developing%20a%20space-based%20anti-satellite%20weapon.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20always%20been%20categorically%20against%20putting%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20Defence%20Minister%20Sergei%20Shoigu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fputin-says-categorically-against-putting-nuclear-weapons-in-space%2Farticleshow%2F107860725.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fputin-says-categorically-against-putting-nuclear-weapons-in-space%2Famp_articleshow%2F107860725.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fputin-says-categorically-against-putting-nuclear-weapons-in-space%2Famp_articleshow%2F107860725.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%98On%20Path%20of%20Peace%E2%80%99%2C%20Modi%20Says%20in%20Jammu%20During%20Inauguration%20Spree%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20212830%2FNarendra-Modi-Jammu-February-2024.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sounding%20the%20poll%20bugle%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2020)%20urged%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(J%26amp%3BK)%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Jammu%E2%80%99s%20Maulana%20Azad%20Stadium%2C%20Modi%20again%20targeted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdynastic%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccorrupt%E2%80%9D%20political%20parties%20for%20%E2%80%9Cplaying%20with%20the%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%E2%80%9D%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20people%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20any%20names%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20his%20speech%20largely%20focused%20on%20the%20developmental%20projects%20completed%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20under%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20new%20legislations%20that%20have%20provided%20political%20reservation%20and%20other%20benefits%20to%20the%20Union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Other%20Backwards%20Classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20downpour%2C%20Modi%20started%20his%20address%20in%20the%20Dogri%20language%20at%20the%20same%20venue%20where%20he%20had%2C%20as%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%2C%20addressed%20the%20%E2%80%98Lalkar%20Rally%E2%80%99%20in%202013%20that%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20for%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20rally%20that%20took%20place%20on%20December%202%2C%202013%2C%20Modi%20said%20he%20had%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20an%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20and%20an%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20(IIM)%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20delivered%20on%20my%20commitment%20with%20both%20IIM%20and%20IIT%20functional%20in%20Jammu%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20consumed%20by%20the%20politics%20of%20hartals%20and%20shutdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20we%20see%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20life%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Those%20who%20ran%20J%26amp%3BK%20for%20decades%20didn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20your%20dreams%20and%20aspirations.%20They%20only%20cared%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20the%20rally%20without%20taking%20any%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20restored%20the%20democratic%20rights%20of%20the%20downtrodden%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20fulfilled%20the%20decades-old%20wish%20of%20the%20Valmiki%20community%20by%20granting%20them%20Scheduled%20Caste%20status.%20Paharis%2C%20Gadda%20Brahmins%2C%20Kolis%20and%20other%20downtrodden%20communities%20have%20been%20included%20in%20the%20ST%20category.%20We%20have%20reserved%20seats%20for%20ST%20categories%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20for%20OBCs%20in%20municipalities.%20We%20are%20taking%20everyone%20along%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20becoming%20a%20centre%20of%20excellence%20in%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20time%20ago%2C%20only%20disappointing%20news%20of%20separatism%2C%20terrorism%2C%20bombing%20and%20kidnapping%20used%20to%20come%20out%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20schools%20used%20to%20be%20burnt.%20Now%2C%20schools%20are%20decorated.%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20on%20the%20path%20of%20peace%2C%20prosperity%20and%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlanked%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20lieutenant%20governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20minister%20of%20state%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Jugal%20Kishore%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Gujjar%20leader%20Gulam%20Ali%20Khatana%2C%20Modi%20said%20there%20were%20only%20four%20medical%20colleges%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20out%20of%20power%20before%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20there%20are%2012%20such%20colleges.%20There%20were%20only%20500%20MBBS%20seats%2C%20but%20today%20there%20are%20over%201%2C300%20MBBS%20seats.%20Not%20a%20single%20seat%20was%20available%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20for%20medical%20students%20to%20pursue%20postgraduate%20degrees.%20Today%20there%20are%20over%20650%20seats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20claimed%20that%20more%20than%20450%20nursing%20colleges%20have%20been%20opened%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20AIIMS%20%5BAll%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%5D%20are%20being%20built%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20of%20which%20I%20will%20have%20the%20honour%20of%20inaugurating%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdream%20come%20true%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20said%20that%20infrastructure-development%20projects%20worth%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20education%2C%20transportation%20and%20energy%20(among%20other)%20sectors%20were%20either%20being%20inaugurated%20or%20that%20their%20foundation%20stones%20were%20laid%20on%20Tuesday%20following%20his%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20virtually%20flagged%20off%20the%20first%20electric%20train%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20train%20service%20between%20Jammu%E2%80%99s%20Sangaldan%20station%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Baramulla%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu-Srinagar%20railway%20line%20is%20scheduled%20to%20get%20completed%20by%20March%20this%20year%2C%20as%20per%20Union%20railway%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%2C%20with%20the%20Ramban-Reasi%20section%20still%20incomplete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20railway%20project%2C%20which%20will%20connect%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20started%20in%201995%20but%20has%20missed%20several%20deadlines%20due%20to%20the%20rugged%20terrain%2C%20which%20cuts%20through%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Pir%20Panjal%20mountain%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20infrastructure%20development%20that%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20day%20is%20not%20far%20when%20people%20will%20sit%20in%20a%20train%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20embark%20on%20a%20journey%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20will%20forget%20Switzerland%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20developmental%20works%20will%20benefit%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20that%20the%20world%20was%20witnessing%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20wall%20of%20%5BArticle%5D%20370%2C%20which%20impeded%20development%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20has%20been%20demolished%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20on%20the%20path%20of%20prosperity.%20The%20power%20of%20370%20is%20such%20that%20after%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20I%20have%20asked%20people%20of%20the%20country%20to%20give%20us%20370%20seats%20while%20the%20NDA%20%5BNational%20Democratic%20Alliance%5D%20will%20cross%20400%20seats%20%5Bin%20the%20upcoming%20elections%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Congress%2C%20Modi%20claimed%20that%20the%20party%20did%20not%20respect%20the%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20government%20kept%20lying%20to%20the%20soldiers%20for%2040%20years%20that%20it%20would%20bring%20the%20%E2%80%98One%20Rank%2C%20One%20Pension%E2%80%99%20(OROP)%20scheme%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20BJP%20which%20fulfilled%20the%20promise.%20Due%20to%20the%20OROP%20scheme%2C%20former%20soldiers%20of%20Jammu%20alone%20have%20received%20over%20Rs%201%2C600%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708445124000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20212830%2FNarendra-Modi-Jammu-February-2024.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjk-on-path-of-peace-modi-says-in-jammu-during-inauguration-spree%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prime%20minister%20said%20the%20world%20was%20witnessing%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%9D%