d%20village%20development%20officer%20(VDO)%20hailing%20from%20the%20Dalit%20Regar%20community%2C%20tragically%20took%20his%20own%20life%20on%20Sunday%2C%20February%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamily%20members%20of%20Lalit%20%E2%80%93%20an%20IIT%20graduate%20with%20aspirations%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20allege%20that%20he%20had%20been%20subjected%20to%20threats.%20Merely%20three%20days%20before%20his%20death%2C%20he%20had%20filed%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20alleging%20corruption%20against%20the%20sarpanch%20of%20Cheeplata%20village%20in%20Neem%20Ka%20Thana%20district%2C%20where%20he%20was%20stationed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sarpanch%20and%20other%20officers%20kept%20putting%20pressure%20on%20Lalit%20to%20get%20work%20done.%20Manoj%20Gurjar%2C%20the%20sarpanch%2C%20his%20father%20and%20former%20sarpanch%2C%20Birbalram%20Gurjar%2C%20and%20the%20then%20Gram%20Sevak%2C%20Narendra%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20were%20also%20harassing%20him%20a%20lot%20because%20he%20filed%20a%20report%20on%20embezzlement%20by%20Singh%20and%20Gurjar%20in%20the%20gram%20panchayat%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20family%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20members%20allege%20that%20ever%20since%20Lalit%20got%20his%20first%20posting%20in%20Cheeplata%2C%20after%20securing%20the%20government%20job%20of%20the%20village%20development%20officer%20in%20April%202023%2C%20he%20was%20stressed%20as%20he%20was%20being%20harassed%20by%20the%20sarpanch%20and%20local%20panchayat%20officials%20because%20of%20his%20honest%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20his%20honest%20nature%2C%20Lalit%20never%20agreed%20to%20do%20anything%20illegal%20and%20would%20stop%20others%20from%20doing%20wrong.%20Ever%20since%20he%20had%20started%20working%20%5Bas%20the%20village%20development%20officer%5D%2C%20he%20was%20being%20harassed%20by%20the%20accused.%20Recently%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20incumbent%20sar