%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20162814%2Fimage-1845.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20162814%2Fimage-1845-300x149.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20162814%2Fimage-1845-1024x507.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698000%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22594%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20scene%20from%20outside%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20where%20villagers%20have%20assembled.%20Photo%20by%20Special%20Arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20brilliant%20student%20with%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20an%20IAS%20officer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%E2%80%99s%20relatives%20say%20that%20ever%20since%20he%20registered%20the%20FIR%2C%20Lalit%20was%20stressed%20as%20he%20started%20receiving%20threats%20to%20withdraw%20the%20case.%20He%20also%20told%20his%20family%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLalit%2C%20a%20brilliant%20student%20who%20attended%20IIT%20and%20aspired%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20officer%2C%20hailed%20from%20a%20family%20where%20his%20parents%20worked%20as%20labourers%20to%20sustain%20the%20household.%20On%20Saturday%20night%20%5BFebruary%2017%5D%2C%20his%20mother%20observed%20him%20writing%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20and%20assumed%20he%20was%20studying.%20Unaware%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20that%20Lalit%20was%20writing%20his%20suicide%20note%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Regar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarly%20on%20Sunday%20morning%20%5BFebruary%2018%5D%2C%20when%20his%20sister%20looked%20through%20the%20window%20of%20his%20room%2C%20she%20saw%20Lalit%20hanging%20from%20the%20ceiling%20fan.%20My%20cousin%20has%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20caste-based%20oppression.%20When%20someone%20like%20Lalit%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20poor%20Dalit%20family%2C%20excels%20in%20their%20career%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20go%20down%20well%20with%20people.%20He%20was%20subjected%20to%20mental%20torture.%20Lalit%20was%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20Dalit%20families%20in%20our%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20was%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20of%20his%20family%2C%20which%20now%20stares%20at%20an%20uncertain%20future%2C%20Regar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20family%20is%20demanding%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20and%20a%20government%20job%20for%20a%20family%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalit%20rights%20activist%20Geegraj%20Jodli%2C%20along%20with%20local%20villagers%2C%20staged%20a%20dharna%20on%20February%2018%20in%20Neem%20Ka%20Thana%2C%20demanding%20justice%20for%20Lalit%2C%20whose%20last%20rites%20were%20conducted%20later%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Regar%20community%20is%20traditionally%20engaged%20in%20shoe%20making%20and%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20among%20the%20most%20marginalised%20Dalit%20communities.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20for%20a%20youngster%20from%20such%20an%20underprivileged%20section%20of%20the%20society%20to%20enrol%20in%20the%20IIT%20or%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20UPSC.%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20death%20shows%20us%20the%20cruel%20face%20of%20the%20feudalism%20ingrained%20in%20the%20society%20as%20he%20died%20because%20of%20caste%20oppression%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Neem%20Ka%20Thana-based%20activist%20Kailash%20Mina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmajoritarian-politics-and-the-plight-of-dalits%5C%22%3EMajoritarian%20Politics%20and%20the%20Plight%20of%20Dalits%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20subjected%20to%20mental%20torture%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20note%20reportedly%20written%20by%20Lalit%2C%20it%20has%20been%20mentioned%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20clear%20the%20UPSC%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Rajendra%20Singh%2C%20circle%20officer%20Ajitgarh%2C%20and%20the%20investigating%20officer%20in%20the%20case%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20suicide%20note%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20forensic%20science%20laboratory%20(FSL)%20to%20confirm%20whether%20it%20has%20been%20written%20by%20Lalit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20an%20IIT%20graduate%20but%20while%20doing%20UPSC%2C%20I%20got%20trapped%20in%20this%20village%20development%20officer%20job%2C%20and%20now%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20do%20UPSC%20or%20anything%20else.%20Above%20all%20this%2C%20they%20pressurise%20me%20too%20much%20and%20nobody%20supports%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20note%20written%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20mentioned%20several%20instances%20wherein%20Lalit%20was%20reportedly%20harassed%20in%20the%20course%20of%20his%20work.%20It%20said%20that%20BDO%20Ajitgarh%20pressurised%20him%20to%20register%20the%20corruption%20FIR%20against%20the%20sarpanch%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20engaged%20in%20any%20corruption%2C%20not%20even%20a%20rupee%E2%80%99s%20worth%2C%20yet%20I%20was%20subjected%20to%20mental%20torture.%20Birbal%20ji%20(the%20father%20of%20the%20current%20sarpanch%20of%20Cheeplata)%20has%20created%20such%20a%20hostile%20environment%20in%20this%20panchayat%20that%20anyone%20wishing%20to%20work%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20so%2C%20and%20he%20has%20never%20allowed%20any%20work%20to%20progress%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EChaar%20mahine%20ho%20gaye%20mujhe%20depression%2C%20anxiety%20se%20jeete%20hue%2C%20ab%20nahin%20jeene.%20Sab%20jhuthe%20hain%20yaar%2C%20koi%20saath%20nahi%20deta.%20I%20am%20sorry%2C%20main%20haar%20gaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%E2%80%99s%20been%20four%20months%20living%20with%20depression%20and%20anxiety%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20on%20anymore%E2%80%A6%20Everybody%20is%20a%20liar.%20No%20one%20supports%20me.%20I%20am%20sorry%2C%20I%20have%20lost)%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmental-health-caste%5C%22%3EWhen%20Mental%20Health%20Collides%20With%20Caste%20Identity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFIR%20registered%20against%20sarpanch%2C%20his%20father%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20his%20relatives%20registered%20an%20FIR%20under%20Sections%20306%20(abetment%20of%20suicide)%20and%20120-B%20(criminal%20conspiracy)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%20on%20February%2018%20at%20the%20Thoi%20police%20station%20under%20Neem%20ka%20Thana%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20accused%20persons%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20including%20Cheeplata%20sarpanch%20Manoj%20Gurjar%2C%20his%20father%20Birbal%20Ram%2C%20Narendra%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20Jagdev%2C%20Pokhar%2C%20Panchayat%20Samiti%20BDO%2C%20and%20Mangal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20contacted%20Ajay%20Singh%20Nathawat%2C%20BDO%2C%20Ajitgarh%20Panchayat%20Samiti%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20family%20of%20pressuring%20him%20to%20register%20the%20corruption%20FIR%2C%20he%20denied%20the%20allegations%20but%20accepted%20that%20Lalit%20had%20met%20him%20on%20February%2015%20and%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLalit%20had%20met%20me%20on%20February%2015%20and%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20resign.%20As%20the%20BDO%2C%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20provide%20counselling%20to%20my%20staff%20and%20find%20out%20what%20is%20the%20reason.%20After%20I%20counseled%20him%2C%20he%20withdrew%20his%20resignation%20and%20I%20assured%20him%20I%20alone%20cannot%20take%20the%20decision%20of%20transferring%20him%20and%20told%20him%20that%20once%20the%20standing%20committee%20of%20the%20Panchayat%20Samiti%20meets%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20he%20is%20transferred%20to%20another%20gram%20panchayat.%20I%20promised%20him%20a%20solution%20by%20Monday.%20As%20for%20Lalit%20filing%20the%20corruption%20FIR%2C%20it%20is%20part%20of%20the%20general%20course%20of%20work%20of%20the%20village%20development%20officer%20to%20register%20FIRs%20in%20matters%20relating%20to%20corruption%20in%20gram%20panchayat%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nathawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20no%20persons%20have%20been%20arrested%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20members%20of%20the%20deceased%20have%20alleged%20that%20Lalit%20died%20by%20suicide%20because%20ever%20since%20he%20had%20filed%20the%20corruption%20FIR%2C%20he%20was%20being%20threatened.%20Among%20those%20booked%20are%20the%20present%20sarpanch%20of%20Cheeplata%20and%20his%20father%2C%20who%20are%20accused%20of%20threatening%20the%20deceased.%20The%20BDO%20has%20also%20been%20booked%20in%20the%20FIR%20because%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20relatives%20allege%20he%20pressured%20him%20to%20register%20the%20FIR.%20So%20far%2C%20no%20arrests%20have%20been%20made.%20We%20are%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20The%20family%20has%20given%20us%20an%20alleged%20suicide%20note%2C%20which%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20forensic%20lab%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20it%20was%20written%20by%20Lalit%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajendra%20Singh%2C%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20and%20circle%20officer%20Ajitgarh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20investigating%20officer%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20know%20someone%20%E2%80%93%20friend%20or%20family%20member%20%E2%80%93%20at%20risk%20of%20suicide%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20them.%20The%20Suicide%20Prevention%20India%20Foundation%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20tabindex%3D%5C%22-1%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spif.in%2Fseek-help%2F%5C%22%