4%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-2-1708432198-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342451%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAvi%20points%20out%20that%20the%20economic%20burden%20was%20the%20major%20factor%20behind%20the%20malnutrition%20crisis%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20nearly%20half%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FMP%2FKatni.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E49.5%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E)%20of%20under-five%20children%20in%20Katni%20suffered%20from%20stunting%20(below-average%20height%20for%20their%20age)%2C%20with%2044%20percent%20of%20these%20children%20also%20being%20underweight%20(weighing%20below%20the%20healthy%20range%20for%20their%20age).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvi%20points%20out%20that%20the%20economic%20burden%20was%20the%20major%20factor%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338306%2Fias-officer-shubham-gupta-used-artificial-intelligence-to-fight-malnutrition-govt-schools-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emalnutrition%20crisis%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20district.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20impoverished%20families%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20a%20nutritious%20diet%20for%20their%20children.%20Although%20the%20Government%20allocates%20additional%20take-home%20rations%20that%20comprise%20wheat%2C%20rice%2C%20or%20grams%20for%20every%20malnourished%20family%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20extra%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avi%2C%20who%20joined%20Katni%20as%20a%20collector%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20young%20kid%20continues%20to%20be%20fed%20a%20poor%20diet%2C%20it%20results%20in%20cognitive%20and%20intellectual%20disabilities%20throughout%20their%20life.%20More%20than%20the%20ration%20support%2C%20I%20had%20understood%20these%20families%20should%20be%20provided%20emotional%20support%20in%20terms%20of%20counselling%20and%20care%2C%20towards%20understanding%20the%20need%20behind%20investing%20in%20their%20child%20in%20the%20initial%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20birthed%20an%20idea%20to%20engage%20the%20community%20to%20combat%20malnutrition%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1-1708432148.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20IAS%20officer%20appealed%20to%20the%20community%20of%20Katni%20to%20adopt%20malnourished%20kids%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20proper%20nutritional%20care.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1-1708432148.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1-1708432148-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1-1708432148-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1-1708432148-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1-1708432148-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20appealed%20to%20the%20community%20to%20adopt%20malnourished%20kids%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20proper%20nutritional%20care.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20community%2C%20by%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20Integrated%20Management%20of%20Acute%20Malnutrition%20(IMAM)%20programme%20of%20the%20Indian%20Government%2C%20which%20provides%20take-home%20rations%20to%20children%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20appealed%20to%20the%20community%20of%20Katni%20to%20adopt%20malnourished%20kids%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20proper%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F114640%2Futtar-pradesh-malnutrition-breast-feeding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enutritional%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20this%20programme%2C%20anyone%20can%20volunteer%20to%20look%20after%20malnourished%20children.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20nutrition%20kits%20for%20at%20least%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%20The%20kits%20comprise%20a%20variety%20of%20vitamin%20and%20protein-rich%20food%20products%20%E2%80%94%20including%20amla%20candy%2C%20soybean%20nuggets%2C%20grams%2C%20%3Cem%3Esattu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Horlicks%2C%20jaggery%2C%20groundnuts%2C%20and%20lentils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20Collector%20roped%20in%20a%20team%20of%20paediatricians%2C%20child%20nutritionists%2C%20and%20experts%20from%20the%20women%20and%20child%20development%20department%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20kit%2C%20specially%20designed%20for%20malnourished%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20providing%20rations%20worth%20Rs%20600%20per%20child%20every%20month.%20This%20ration%20kit%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20provided%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20month.%20The%20additional%20ration%20support%20was%20given%20for%20three%20to%20six%20months%20to%20MAM%20%5Bmod