in%20the%20nutrition%20level%20of%20SAM%20and%20MAM%20children%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20programme%2C%20the%20district%20was%20able%20to%20adopt%20around%20600%20malnourished%20children.%20But%20we%20still%20have%20at%20least%201%2C000%20malnourished%20children%20in%20our%20district.%20Of%20these%2C%2050%20are%20severely%20SAM%20kids.%20In%20the%20second%20phase%2C%20we%20will%20try%20to%20bring%20this%20number%20to%20a%20minimum%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20IAS%20Avi%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20IAS%20officer%2C%20the%20results%20of%20the%20initiative%20have%20brought%20immense%20contentment.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20satisfying%20as%20well%20as%20a%20learning%20experience%20for%20us.%20We%20could%20have%20done%20this%20work%20through%20Government%20finances%2C%20but%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20programme%20was%20ensured%20as%20the%20community%20was%20involved.%20The%20community%20mobilisation%20will%20also%20ensure%20that%20this%20work%20keeps%20on%20going%2C%20irrespective%20of%20who%20the%20officer%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20takes%20just%20Rs%20600%20to%20sponsor%20nutritional%20meals%20for%20one%20malnourished%20child.%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20contribute%2C%20here%20are%20the%20bank%20account%20details%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAtal%20Bal%20Mitra%20Yojana%3Cbr%3EBank%20account%20number%3A%2040560100000070%3Cbr%3EIFSC%20code%3A%20BARB0INDKAT%3Cbr%3EBank%20of%20Baroda%2C%20Industrial%20area%2C%20Katni.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20details%2C%20you%20can%20also%20contact%20Nayan%20Singh%2C%20district%20programme%20officer%2C%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20department%2C%20Katni%2C%20at%20%2B91%2096309%2081671.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20office%2C%20Katni%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3