re%20they%20sought%20refuge%2C%20or%20while%20fleeing.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20reportedly%20holding%20white%20pieces%20of%20cloth%20when%20they%20were%20killed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%20or%20affiliated%20forces%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20experts%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F02%2Fisraelopt-un-experts-appalled-reported-human-rights-violations-against%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20voiced%20serious%20concern%20about%20the%20arbitrary%20detention%20of%20hundreds%20of%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20including%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20journalists%20and%20humanitarian%20workers%2C%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20conflict%20on%20October%207%20following%20the%20deadly%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20detainees%20have%20reportedly%20been%20subjected%20to%20inhuman%20and%20degrading%20treatment%2C%20denied%20menstruation%20pads%2C%20food%20and%20medicine%2C%20and%20severely%20beaten%2C%20they%20said.%20Furthermore%2C%20on%20at%20least%20one%20occasion%2C%20Palestinian%20women%20detained%20in%20Gaza%20were%20allegedly%20kept%20in%20a%20cage%20in%20the%20rain%20and%20cold%2C%20without%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIsrael%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%2FoPt%3A%20UN%20experts%20appalled%20by%20egregious%20human%20rights%20violations%20to%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPalestinian%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Palestinian%3C%2Fa%3E%20women%20%26amp%3B%20girls%20continue%20to%20be%20subjected%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaza%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26amp%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWestBank%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WestBank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20incl.%20credible%20reports%20of%20arbitrary%20executions%2C%20sexual%20assault%20%26amp%3B%20other%20degrading%20treatments%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fag9r3kVJkQ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fag9r3kVJkQ%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGfdqCTX3yv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FGfdqCTX3yv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UN%20Special%20Procedures%20(%40UN_SPExperts)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_SPExperts%2Fstatus%2F1759531255337467916%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESexual%20assault%20in%20detention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20particularly%20distressed%20by%20reports%20that%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20girls%20in%20detention%20have%20also%20been%20subjected%20to%20multiple%20forms%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20such%20as%20being%20stripped%20naked%20and%20searched%20by%20male%20Israeli%20army%20officers.%20At%20least%20two%20female%20Palestinian%20detainees%20were%20reportedly%20raped%20while%20others%20were%20reportedly%20threatened%20with%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhotos%20of%20women%20detainees%20in%20degrading%20circumstances%20were%20also%20%E2%80%9Creportedly%20taken%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%E2%80%9D%20and%20uploaded%20online%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20were%20also%20concerned%20that%20an%20unknown%20number%20of%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20children%2C%20including%20girls%2C%20have%20reportedly%20gone%20missing%20after%20contact%20with%20the%20Israeli%20army%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20disturbing%20reports%20of%20at%20least%20one%20female%20infant%20forcibly%20transferred%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%20into%20Israel%2C%20and%20of%20children%20being%20separated%20from%20their%20parents%2C%20whose%20whereabouts%20remain%20unknown%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECall%20for%20probe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20remind%20the%20Government%20of%20Israel%20of%20its%20obligation%20to%20uphold%20the%20right%20to%20life%2C%20safety%2C%20health%2C%20and%20dignity%20of%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20girls%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20is%20subjected%20to%20violence%2C%20torture%2C%20ill-treatment%20or%20degrading%20treatment%2C%20including%20sexual%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rights%20experts%20called%20for%20an%20independent%2C%20impartial%2C%20prompt%2C%20thorough%20and%20effective%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegations%20and%20for%20Israel%20to%20cooperate%20with%20any%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTaken%20together%2C%20these%20alleged%20acts%20may%20constitute%20grave%20violations%20of%20international%20human%20rights%20and%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20and%20amount%20to%20serious%20crimes%20under%20international%20criminal%20law%20that%20could%20be%20prosecuted%20under%20the%20Rome%20Statute%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rome%20Statute%20is%20the%20July%201998%20treaty%20that%20established%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icc-cpi.int%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Criminal%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(ICC)%2C%20which%20investigates%20and%20tries%20individuals%20charged%20with%20genocide%2C%20war%20crimes%2C%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20and%20the%20crime%20of%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependent%20voices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20was%20issued%20by%20Reem%20Alsalem%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fspecial-procedures%2Fsr-violence-against-women%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpecial%20Rapporteur%20on%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20its%20causes%20and%20consequences%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Francesca%20Albanese%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fspecial-procedures%2Fsr-palestine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpecial%20Rapporteur%20on%20the%20situation%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alongside%20the%20members%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fspecial-procedures%2Fwg-women-and-girls%2Fmembers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUN%20Working%20group%20on%20discrimination%20against%20women%20and%20girls%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Dorothy%20Estrada%20Tanck%20(Chair)%2C%20Claudia%20Flores%2C%20Ivana%20Krsti%C4%87%2C%20Haina%20Lu%2C%20and%20Laura%20Nyirinkindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20Rapporteurs%20and%20independent%20experts%20are%20appointed%20by%20the%20UN%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2FHRBodies%2FHRC%2FPages%2FHome.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman%20Rights%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20report%20and%20advise%20on%20specific%20thematic%20issues%20or%20country%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20work%20on%20a%20voluntary%20basis%20and%20are%20independent%20of%20any%20government%20or%20organisation.%C2%A0%20They%20serve%20in%20their%20individual%20capacity%20and%20are%20not%20UN%20staff%20and%20do%20not%20receive%20payment%20for%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146667%5C%22%3EUN%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708434020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-co