y%20match%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20in%20a%20video%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%20-%20in%20response%20to%20a%20growing%20backlash%20over%20his%20absence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flionel-messi-explains-hong-kong-no-show-in-video-to-fans-as-backlash-grows-13076108%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flionel-messi-explains-hong-kong-no-show-in-video-to-fans-as-backlash-grows-13076108%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flionel-messi-explains-hong-kong-no-show-in-video-to-fans-as-backlash-grows-13076108%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Economics%20of%20Coaching%20Classes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19124917%2Fankita-konwar-zn9QqA-JTmY-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarkets%20are%20acclaimed%20to%20give%20perfect%20solutions%20that%20satisfy%20both%20the%20consumer%20and%20the%20producer.%20They%20are%20said%20to%20bring%20together%20%E2%80%98all%20those%20who%20are%20willing%20and%20able%20to%20pay%E2%80%99%20with%20%E2%80%98all%20those%20who%20are%20willing%20and%20able%20to%20sell%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20certain%20price%20called%20the%20equilibrium%20price.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20situation%20of%20market%20equilibrium%2C%20that%20almost%20sounds%20platonic%2C%20several%20contentious%20questions%20emerge.%20Is%20everyone%20willing%20to%20pay%3F%20Who%20is%20not%20able%20to%20pay%3F%20Does%20it%20matter%3F%20Do%20they%20know%20what%20they%20are%20paying%20for%3F%20Who%20is%20the%20producer%3F%20Is%20profit%20their%20only%20motive%3F%20Obscure%20answers%20to%20these%20questions%20have%20led%20economists%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98invisible%20hand%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20market%20may%20not%20always%20be%20the%20best%20way%20to%20organise%20economic%20activity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarkets%20work%20efficiently%20for%20ordinary%20goods%20like%20online%20taxi%20services%20and%20even%20in%20case%20of%20%E2%80%98bads%E2%80%99%20such%20as%20tobacco%2C%20logical%20solutions%20are%20provided%20by%20the%20market.%20However%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20in%20question%20is%20education%20and%20the%20agents%20providing%20it%20are%20the%20coaching%20centres.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20getting%20into%20the%20philosophical%20debate%20on%20what%20is%20education%2C%20we%20look%20at%20this%20fairly%20complex%20good%20from%20an%20economist%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20and%20question%20the%20efficiency%20of%20coaching%20classes%20and%20how%20much%20well-being%20they%20actually%20produce%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEducation%20in%20itself%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20school%20level%2C%20is%20declared%20to%20be%20a%20public%20good%20which%20is%20non-excludable%20and%20non-rival.%20This%20means%20that%20nobody%20should%20be%20excluded%20from%20its%20consumption%20and%20consumption%20by%20one%20should%20not%20rival%20the%20other%E2%80%99s.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20private%20schools%20occupying%2031.5%25%20of%20the%20total%20schools%2C%2046.7%25%20in%20total%20enrolments%20and%2049.3%25%20of%20total%20teachers%20in%20India%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98public%20good%E2%80%99%20nature%20of%20education%20becomes%20blurred.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrivate%20schooling%20is%20both%20excludable%20and%20rival.%20As%20if%20this%20complexity%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20shadow%20schooling%20in%20the%20form%20of%20coaching%20centres%20have%20mushroomed%20all%20over%20the%20country%20to%20meet%20an%20unprecedented%20demand.%20The%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20round%20of%20the%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20(NSS%202017)%20states%20that%2027.2%25%20of%20students%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%2038.3%25%20of%20urban%20students%20take%20private%20tuitions%20at%20the%20secondary%20level.%20The%202022%20ASER%20report%20states%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20rural%20Indian%20students%20between%20grades%201%20to%208%20taking%20private%20tuition%20classes%20increased%20from%2026.4%25%20in%202018%20to%2030.5%25%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20genesis%20of%20a%20massive%20and%20progressively%20increasing%20demand%20for%20private%20coaching%20is%20the%20substandard%20state%20of%20government%20school%20education.%20Nearly%2035%25%20of%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20students%20report%20this%20as%20the%20reason%20to%20opt%20for%20private%20schooling%2C%20according%20to%20NSSO%20data.%20The%20share%20of%20government%20schooling%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20schooling%20is%20higher%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20at%2068%25%20at%20the%20secondary%20and%20higher%20secondary%20level%3B%20than%20in%20urban%20areas%20where%20the%20same%20is%20at%2038.8%25%20explaining%20the%20increasing%20demand%20for%20private%20coaching.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20thriving%20coaching%20culture%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%20has%20emerged%20in%20a%20country%20that%E2%80%99s%20obsessed%20with%20entrance%20exams.%20Appearing%20as%20%E2%80%98ancillary%20units%E2%80%99%20of%20private%20schools%2C%20coaching%20centres%20have%20witnessed%20a%20phenomenal%20growth%20with%20some%20becoming%20unicorns%20and%20case%20studies%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rising%20feeling%20of%20irrelevance%20of%20schools%20%E2%80%93%20since%20they%20do%20not%20provide%20the%20code%20to%20crack%20entrance%20exams%20%E2%80%93%20has%20made%20parents%20and%20students%20flock%20to%20private%20coaching%20centres%20to%20fill%20that%20gap.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%20what%20sounds%20like%20a%20simple%20story%20of%20effective%20demand%20in%20economics%20takes%20a%20twist%20because%20of%20the%20original%20nature%20of%20education%20as%20a%20public%20good%20that%20we%20began%20with.%20Public%20goods%20create%20%E2%80%98externalities%E2%80%99%20or%20spillover%20effects%20that%20affect%20the%20society%20positively%20apart%20from%20benefitting%20the%20consumers%20themselves.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEducation%2C%20justifiably%2C%20has%20several%20positive%20spillovers%20that%20may%20or%20may%20not%20recognised%20by%20an%20individual%20compelling%20the%20government%20to%20make%20basic%20schooling%20not%20only%20free%20but%20also%20compulsory.%20Occasionally%2C%20however%2C%20a%20public%20good%20can%20turn%20into%20a%20public%20bad%20when%20they%20give%20rise%20to%20negative%20externalities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrivate%20coaching%2C%20that%20was%20originally%20intended%20to%20compliment%20school%20education%20has%20almost%20become%20a%20%E2%80%98substitute%20good%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20private%20schools%20in%20the%20country%20that%20admit%20students%20without%20expecting%20them%20to%20be%20physically%20present.%20Emergence%20of%20coaching%20classes%20have%20turned%20mainstream%20schools%20into%20%E2%80%98dummy%E2%80%99%20schools%2C%20allowing%20students%20to%20only%20attend%20science%20practical%20classes%20and%20appear%20for%20exams.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anticipated%20high%20rates%20of%20return%20through%20private%20coaching%20gives%20ground%20for%20the%20steep%20investment%20in%20it%2C%20overlooking%20several%20negative%20externalities%20that%20have%20been%20internalised%20by%20the%20stakeholders%20especially%20parents.%20Charging%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20hour%2C%20private%20coaching%20makes%20up%20for%20the%20third%20biggest%20component%20of%20household%20expenditure%20on%20education.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20fervent%20%E2%80%98neighbourhood%20effect%E2%80%99%20stating%20how%20consumer%20preferences%20are%20influenced%20by%20surroundings%2C%20seems%20to%20govern%20household%20decisions%20on%20consuming%20private%20coaching%20and%20with%20asymmetric%20information%20and%20uncertainty%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20lack%20of%20clear%20understanding%20of%20student%E2%80%99s%20own%20genuine%20interest%2C%20aptitude%20and%20inclination%20to%20pursue%20a%20certain%20course%20in%20future%2C%20it%20may%20result%20in%20suboptimal%20consumer%20choices.%20Massive%20advertising%20and%20aggressive%20marketing%20by%20coaching%20centres%20seems%20to%20have%20multiplied%20the%20demand%20for%20them%20validating%20the%20economic%20principle%20%E2%80%9CSupply%20creates%20its%20own%20demand%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20externalities%20in%20case%20of%20private%20coaching%20are%20not%20immediately%20obvious%20as%20in%20a%20pollution%20emitting%20industry.%20The%20rise%20in%20dummy%20schools%2C%20extensive%20commercialisation%20of%20education%2C%20excessive%20focus%20on%20exams%20over%20actual%20learning%2C%20relentless%20scurrying%20of%20young%20children%20between%20school%20and%20coaching%20with%20little%20time%20for%20free%20play%20and%20finally%20increasing%20mental%20health%20issues%20among%20teenagers%20leading%20to%20growing%20suicide%20numbers%20are%20some%20of%20these%20problems.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Kota%2C%20the%20hub%20of%20private%20coaching%2C%20is%20infamous%20in%20reporting%2020-25%20cases%20of%20young%20students%20dying%20by%20suicide%20in%20fear%20of%20not%20fulfilling%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20aspirations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudents%20accounted%20for%208%25%20of%20the%20total%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20in%202022%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau.%20Of%20these%2C%20most%20of%20the%20students%20were%20in%20higher%20secondary%20school.%20This%20loss%20of%20potential%20human%20capital%20plus%20loss%20of%20productivity%20among%20related%20family%20members%20due%20to%20acute%20distress%20appear%20intangible%20although%20real.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Tilak%2C%20an%20eminent%20researcher%20in%20the%20field%20of%20education%20talks%20of%20three%20%E2%80%98fads%E2%80%99%20in%20education%3A%20Private%20education%20is%20most%20efficient%2C%20English-medium%20education%20is%20very%20important%20and%20pre-primary%20education%20is%20essential.%20Tilak%20argues%20that%20all%20these%20%E2%80%98fads%E2%80%99%20are%20mere%20views%20of%20people%20that%20lack%20research%20evidence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20private%20coaching%20is%20a%20sure%20road%20to%20success%20can%20be%20annexed%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98fads%E2%80%99%20list.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20IIT-Madras%20study%20revealed%20that%2050%25%20of%20students%20who%20got%20admission%20into%20IITs%20did%20not%20go%20to%20any%20coaching.%20The%20recent%20case%20of%20a%20missing%20teenager%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20who%20feared%20being%20reprimanded%20by%20parents%20for%20his%20poor%20performance%20in%20a%20coaching%20centre%2C%20created%20furore%20in%20society%2C%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20introduce%20more%20regulation%20on%20private%20coaching.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECertainly%20government%20intervention%20is%20needed%20to%20correct%20%E2%80%98market%20failures%E2%80%99%3B%20in%20our%20case%20the%20failure%20of%20achieving%20welfare%20objectives%20intended%20through%20education.%20However%2C%20all%20regulation%20will%20be%20ineffective%20till%20the%20most%20important%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20parents%2C%20are%20fully%20convinced.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%20the%20risk%20taken%20by%20parents%20while%20perceiving%20education%20as%20a%20capital%20good%20and%20the%20joy%20and%20satisfaction%20experienced%20by%20students%20who%20are%20consuming%20it%2C%20there%20are%20externalities%2C%20positive%20and%20negative.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20recognize%20and%20educate%20that%20education%20is%20a%20good%20where%20the%20impact%20is%20on%20parents%20(through%20fees)%2C%20incidence%20in%20on%20students%20(through%20their%20schooling%20experience)%20and%20the%20effects%20are%20on%20the%20society%20(that%20could%20be%20positive%20or%20negative).%20Well-informed%20choices%20of%20parents%2C%20in%20clear%20recognition%20of%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20interests%20and%20abilities%20will%20alone%20bring%20about%20the%20desired%20outcomes%20benefitting%20individually%20and%20collectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Pushkarni%20Panchamukhi%20is%20associate%20dean%20at%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20RV%20University%2C%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708426805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19124917%2Fankita-konwar-zn9QqA-JTmY-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-economics-of-coaching-classes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20thriving%20coaching%20culture%20in%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%20has%20emerged%20in%20a%20country%20that's%20obsessed%20with%20entrance%20exams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-economics-of-coaching-classes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20denies%20claims%20that%20Alexei%20Navalny%20was%20poisoned%20with%20novichok%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708425540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-alexei-navalny-vladimir-putin_6457936.jpg%3F20240216151055%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalny-russia-denies-claims-that-putin-critic-was-poisoned-with-novichok-13076085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20denied%20claims%20made%20by%20Alexei%20Navalny's%20widow%20that%20he%20was%20poisoned%20by%20the%20nerve%20agent%20novichok.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A215%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalny-russia-denies-claims-that-putin-critic-was-poisoned-with-novichok-13076085%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalny-russia-denies-claims-that-putin-critic-was-poisoned-with-novichok-13076085%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalny-russia-denies-claims-that-putin-critic-was-poisoned-with-novichok-13076085%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Of%20Shared%20Stories%20and%20a%20Generation%20Adrift%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20135637%2FUntitled-design-9-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20used%20to%20be%20a%20god-knows-how-many-years-old%20saint%20known%20as%20Paramhansa%20Baba%20in%20the%20town.%20He%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20time%20under%20an%20old%20banyan%20tree%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebagiyaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20adjoining%20the%20British-era%20railway%20station.%20He%20was%20always%20surrounded%20by%20lots%20of%20people%2C%20devotees%2C%20and%20self-appointed%20disciples%2C%20but%20no%20one%20ever%20saw%20him%20speaking.%20He%20occasionally%20ate%20whatever%20people%20offered%20him.%20There%20was%20no%20clear%20pattern%20though%20that%20one%20could%20discern%20from%20when%20he%20accepted%20offerings%2C%20what%20he%20accepted%20as%20offerings%2C%20and%20whose%20offerings%20he%20accepted.%20The%20randomisation%20seems%20to%20have%20added%20to%20his%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmma%20once%20asked%20me%20to%20take%20her%20to%20the%20ashram%20that%20had%20grown%20around%20the%20Paramhansa.%20She%20stopped%20when%20we%20reached%20a%20point%20from%20where%20we%20could%20see%20the%20saint.%20I%20had%20assumed%20that%20she%20would%20want%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20in%20the%20ashram.%20Before%20I%20could%20ask%2C%20she%20explained%20that%20we%20should%20not%20disturb%20saints%20as%20they%20are%20always%20immersed%20in%20meditation.%20We%20left%20a%20few%20minutes%20later.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20and%20last%20time%20I%20had%20a%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20a%20Paramhansa%2C%20even%20if%20from%20a%20distance.%20But%20we%20had%20grown%20up%20hearing%20tales%20of%20Paramhansas%20and%20other%20saints%20who%20dwelled%20in%20our%20district%20and%20the%20neighbouring%20Gwalior%20during%20the%20early%2020th%20century.%20Our%20menfolk%20had%20served%20the%20princely%20state%20in%20various%20capacities%20and%20treated%20the%20village%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20tales%20from%20there%2C%20including%20the%20ones%20featuring%20Paramhansas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20fixed%20points%20of%20a%20Paramhansa%20tale%20included%20his%20(always%20a%20male)%20dramatic%20spiritual%20transformation%20(leaving%20us%20wondering%20why%20similar%20encounters%20did%20not%20awaken%20us)%20and%20the%20idiosyncrasies%20that%20set%20him%20apart%20from%20other%20saints.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20Paramhansas%2C%20there%20were%20other%20saintly%20figures.%20Khatkhata%20Baba%2C%20a%20bureaucrat%20turned%20ascetic.%20Dinanath%20Baba%2C%20a%20soldier%20turned%20ascetic.%20A%20gentle%20Mahamandaleshwar%20who%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20our%20village.%20An%20enigmatic%20fakir%20who%20occasionally%20visited%20the%20village%20but%20disappeared%20after%20curing%20a%20child%20of%20chronic%20knee%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressive%20Parshuramas%20complemented%20reticent%20Paramhansas%20in%20this%20world.%20Ramlila%20was%20a%20major%20cultural%20event%20and%20%3Cem%3EParshurami%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20among%20its%20highlights.%20Parshuramas%20were%20groomed%20in%20%3Cem%3Eakharas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20were%20teachers.%20When%20Parshurama%20entered%20Raja%20Janaka%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20during%20Sita%20Svyamvar%20he%20supposedly%20thundered%20and%20stomped.%20The%20stage%20ought%20to%20creak%20when%20a%20credible%20Parshurama%20stomps.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20understand%20why%20only%20wrestlers%20would%20fit%20this%20role%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20expected%20to%20cultivate%20an%20interest%20in%20Tulsi%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20would%20laugh%20remembering%20how%20an%20itinerant%20Parshurama%20was%20embarrassed%20when%20he%20kept%20stomping%2C%20but%20the%20stage%20stood%20like%20a%20rock%20because%20it%20was%20built%20using%20the%20%3Cem%3Etakht%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20such%20and%20such%20person.%20That%20%3Cem%3Etakht%3C%2Fem%3E%20acquired%20an%20aura%20of%20its%20own%20and%20remained%20unbeatable%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20daily%20routine%20of%20those%20devoted%20to%20wrestling%20and%20their%20successes%20was%20recalled%20in%20great%20detail.%20Children%20would%20hear%20with%20both%20amazement%20and%20irritation%20how%20wrestlers%20drank%20buckets%20full%20of%20milk%20in%20the%20morning.%20Some%20even%20had%20a%20buffalo%20to%20themselves%20and%20allegedly%20drank%20milk%20until%20it%20flowed%20out%20of%20their%20nostrils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamlila%2C%20Ramayana%20path%2C%20and%20Bhagvata%20path%20were%20also%20occasions%20for%20collective%20deliberation%20on%20finer%20points%20of%20literature%20and%20life.%20Many%20of%20the%20celebrated%20participants%20in%20these%20conversations%20had%20learnt%20the%20texts%20such%20as%20Ramacharitmanas%20just%20by%20virtue%20of%20having%20sat%20through%20recitations%20since%20childhood.%20These%20non-literate%20savants%20would%20spend%20whole%20nights%20debating%20a%20couplet%20or%20two.%20(Their%20college-educated%20grandchildren%20struggle%20to%20string%20together%20140%20characters.)%20Stories%20told%20and%20debated%20in%20these%20gatherings%20became%20part%20of%20the%20collective%20wisdom%20of%20the%20village%20and%20it%20turned%20to%20them%20in%20case%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Edharma%20sankat%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20stories%20were%20built%20around%20spiritual%20or%20mythological%20characters%20though.%20Feasts%20were%20another%20highlight%20of%20village%20life.%20Voracious%20eaters%2C%20generous%20hosts%20and%20great%20cooks%20were%20heroes%20of%20many%20a%20story.%20A%20host%20locked%20up%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebaaraat%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20his%20large%20compound%20and%20fed%20them%20over%20several%20days%20until%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20eat%20anymore.%20A%20gentleman%20with%20a%20voracious%20appetite%20could%20be%20satisfied%20by%20only%20two%20households%20in%20the%20entire%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20was%20in%20turn%20nested%20in%20a%20larger%20universe%20that%20included%20other%20neighbouring%20villages%20that%20belonged%20to%20%3Cem%3Ebrothers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20partook%20in%20our%20stories%20and%20contributed%20to%20our%20pool%20of%20stories.%20These%20villages%20shared%20a%20three-tiered%20origin%20myth%20beginning%20with%20their%20displacement%20a%20millennium%20ago%20from%20a%20distant%20land%20in%20the%20wider%20%3Cem%3EBraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20region%20culminating%20in%20their%20eventual%20settlement%20at%20their%20respective%20present%20sites%20before%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20British.%20The%20village%20was%20also%20bound%20through%20marriage%20to%20a%20wider%20network%20of%20villages%20around%20the%20Yamuna%20and%20its%20tributaries%20that%20further%20enriched%20the%20pool%20of%20stories.%20Occasionally%2C%20influences%20from%20beyond%20intersected%20this%20universe.%20Swami%20Dayanand%20Saraswati%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebrother%3C%2Fem%3E%20village%E2%80%99s%20titular%20family%20whose%20path%20later%20also%20crossed%20that%20of%20Motilal%20Nehru.%20Stories%20for%20another%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stories%20are%20our%20(lived%20and)%20remembered%20world.%20Even%20those%20of%20us%20who%20were%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20distant%20towns%20belonged%20to%20this%20world%20because%20they%20were%20raised%20on%20a%20regular%20diet%20of%20these%20stories.%20The%20stories%20served%20as%20the%20bedrock%20of%20our%20faith%20that%20otherwise%20did%20not%20have%20visible%20anchors%20as%20there%20has%20never%20been%20a%20temple%20%3Cem%3Ewithin%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20village.%20(A%20century%20or%20two%20old%20%3Cem%3Echabutra%2Fplatform%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20village%20though%20has%20retained%20an%20assortment%20of%20small%20unrecognisable%20fragments%20of%20a%20medieval%20Hindu%20or%20Jain%20temple.%20Also%2C%20there%20are%20two%20minimalist%20platforms%20dedicated%20to%20Hanuman%20%3Cem%3Eoutside%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20village.)%20The%20hearth%20and%20tulsi%20at%20home%2C%20a%20banyan%20in%20the%20village%20and%20a%20peepal%20in%20the%20fields%20served%20as%20our%20axis%20mundi%2C%20with%20the%20world%20of%20stories%20wrapped%20around%20them%20like%20amma%E2%80%99s%20cotton%20saree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221107%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM.png%201107w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM-300x166.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM-1024x568.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20LivinTheDream%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20newer%20urban%20homes%2C%20each%20of%20us%20populated%20the%20space%20around%20our%20axis%20mundi%20with%20seemingly%20unconnected%20things.%20A%20dargah%20in%20Nagore%20and%20a%20church%20in%20Trivandrum%2C%20the%20grand%20Srirangam%20and%20a%20barely%20noticed%20roadside%20temple%20in%20Old%20Delhi%2C%20a%20Gupta%20temple%20in%20Lalitpur%20and%20a%20village%20deity%20in%20Jaisalmer%2C%20a%20ziarat%20in%20Budgam%20and%20an%20asthan%20in%20Sopore%2C%20a%20monastery%20in%20Leh%20and%20a%20Gurdwara%20in%20Kargil%2C%20sacred%20trees%20in%20Senapati%20and%20Niuland%2C%20a%20courtyard%20of%20a%20goddess%20in%20Srinagar%20and%20a%20church%20in%20Pungro.%20All%20these%20and%20much%20more%20fit%20in%20effortlessly%20in%20the%20small%20but%20capacious%20world%20conjured%20by%20rustic%20storytellers%2C%20who%20had%20not%20heard%20of%20most%20of%20these%20places.%20The%20world%20they%20built%20is%20like%20our%20puja%20ghars%20where%2033%20crore%20gods%20and%20memorabilia%20from%20their%20tirthas%20quietly%20squeeze%20in%20without%20complaints.%20It%20is%20like%20Amma%E2%80%99s%20tiny%20cot%20that%20accommodated%20the%20five%20of%20us.%20In%20that%20matchbox-sized%20space%2C%20time%20stood%20still%20in%20the%20punishing%20summers%20of%20the%20north.%20There%20she%20wove%20bizarre%20tales%20of%20epic%20proportions%20spanning%20ages%20and%20universes%2C%20featuring%20gods%2C%20ghosts%2C%20and%20gentlemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20storytellers%20built%20a%20world%20with%20a%20small%20number%20of%20mostly%20implausible%20tales%2C%20which%20were%20told%20and%20retold%20innumerable%20times%20till%20no%20one%20knew%20or%20cared%20what%20the%20original%20or%20the%20origin%20was.%20It%20was%20often%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20storytellers%20used%20local%20tales%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20gaps%20in%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata%20or%20used%20the%20latter%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20gaps%20in%20the%20local%20tales.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20the%20world%20of%20stories%20we%20inherited%20easily%20accommodates%20both%20the%20unknown%20and%20the%20unknowable.%20And%20it%20is%20to%20this%20world%20that%20we%20turn%20to%20when%20we%20find%20ourselves%20in%20times%20of%20trouble.%20These%20shared%20stories%20are%20the%20means%20through%20which%20we%20understand%20ourselves%20and%20the%20world%20around%20us.%20Until%20a%20decade%20or%20two%20ago%2C%20outsiders%20understood%20us%20as%20the%20sum%20of%20our%20personal%20idiosyncrasies%20and%20the%20stories%20told%20in%20and%20about%20our%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bedrock%20of%20our%20faith%2C%20these%20stories%20survived%20the%20last%20century.%20But%2C%20perhaps%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20ages%2C%20the%20older%20generation%20has%20begun%20to%20forget%20the%20stories%20even%20before%20having%20been%20able%20to%20groom%20storytellers%20among%20their%20grandchildren%2C%20who%20have%20been%20claimed%20by%20urban%20dreams%20sustained%20on%20maddening%20inputs%20of%20men%20and%20material.%20Completely%20oblivious%20of%20the%20enormous%20cultural%20loss%20and%20ill-equipped%20to%20imagine%20alternatives%2C%20the%20grandchildren%20are%20adrift%20and%20clutch%20at%20whatever%20comes%20their%20way%20or%20is%20hurled%20at%20them%20%E2%80%93%20imagined%20nations%2C%20enumerated%20faiths%2C%20purported%20mother%20tongues%20and%20careerism-cum-consumerism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVikas%20Kumar%20teaches%20economics%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fnumbers-as-political-allies%2F4FB6F90A77F38501629062AA2DD4DA1C%5C%22%3ENumbers%20as%20Political%20Allies%3A%20The%20Census%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0(Cambridge%20University%20Press%2C%202023).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708425029000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20135637%2FUntitled-design-9-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fof-shared-stories-and-a-generation-adrift%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shared%20stories%20that%20formed%20the%20bedrock%20of%20our%20faith%20are%20now%20wiped%20out%20from%20public%20memory.%20What%