%3E%20would%20be%20a%20good%20name.%20I%20set%20up%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20pages.%20I%20bought%20jars%20and%20got%20labels%20printed.%20We%20put%20up%2010%20posts%20online%2C%20ran%20a%20few%20Whatsapp%20ads%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20200%20per%20day%2C%20and%20within%20a%20few%20days%2C%20we%20got%2030%20orders%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20just%20the%20mango%20pickle%2C%20they%20soon%20introduced%20more%20pickles%20like%20green%20chilli%2C%20lemon%2C%20mixed%20vegetable%2C%20and%20sweet%20mangoes.%20Amit%20says%20that%20their%20products%20are%20cheaper%20than%20others%20available%20on%20the%20market.%20They%20sell%20trial%20packs%20of%20four%20pickles%20of%20100%20gm%20each%20at%20Rs%20299.%20Another%20hot%20seller%20is%20the%20combo%20pack%20of%20four%20200%20gm%20pickles%20which%20each%20sells%20for%20Rs%20349.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20bestseller%2C%20the%20mango%20pickle%2C%20sells%20for%20Rs%20199%20for%20a%20200%20gm%20pack%2C%20Rs%20299%20for%20400%20gm%20and%20Rs%20599%20for%20800%20gm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaroj%20says%20that%20all%20pickles%20are%20made%20by%20her%20using%20traditional%20recipes%20passed%20on%20to%20her%20by%20her%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20make%20the%20spice%20mix%20myself%20and%20buy%20the%20mangoes%20and%20vegetables%20locally.%20All%20pickles%20are%20made%20without%20chemicals%20and%20preservatives.%20We%20sun-dry%20the%20pickles%20and%20store%20them%20in%20%3Cem%3Ebarnis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditional%20jars)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20200%20orders%20were%20made%20and%20packaged%20at%20home%20itself%2C%20by%20Saroj.%20As%20orders%20increased%2C%20they%20needed%20a%20bigger%20space.%20They%20set%20up%20the%20Moms%20Magic%20Pickle%20India%20unit%20at%20an%20empty%20space%20owned%20by%20her%20husband%20in%20Shadora%20itself.%20They%20also%20called%20local%20women%20to%20he