484%2Fmom-guilt-traveling-with-kid-moushmi-kapadia-vedansh-rigid-spine-muscular-dystrophy-rare-disease-trek-bike-travel-mother%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emother%20to%20go%20ahead%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20my%20entire%20life%20ahead%20of%20me.%20First%2C%20I%20want%20my%20parents%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20mother%20and%20son%20are%20the%20perfect%20blend%20of%20passion%2C%20a%20traditional%20skill%20and%20new%20age%20marketing%20that%20makes%20their%20brand%20a%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20purchase%20Moms%20Magic%20Pickle%20through%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmomsmagicpickleindia.com%2Fproduct%2Fpure-homemade-mango-pickle-%25e2%2594%2582aam-ka-achar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20via%20Whatsapp.%20They%20are%20soon%20planning%20to%20expand%20to%20Amazon%20and%20Flipkart%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708352371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342261%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ith%20her%20son%20Amit's%20help%2C%20Saroj%20Prajapati%20started%20Mom%E2%80%99s%20Magic%20Pickle%20India%20from%20her%20kitchen%20in%20Ashok%20Nagar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Saroj%2C%20a%20homemaker%20who%20had%20never%20even%20attended%20school%2C%20now%20provides%20employment%20to%2030%20local%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20IAS%20Officer%20Spearheaded%20the%20Resolution%20of%2050%2C000%20Pending%20Cases%20In%20Just%204%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20family%20of%20Laxmi%20Yadav%2C%20hailing%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20belonging%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%2C%20has%20been%20navigating%20the%20bureaucratic%20hurdles%20at%20the%20Basti%20district%20collectorate.%20Their%20aim%3F%20To%20secure%20permission%20to%20sell%20their%201.5%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eland%20to%20an%20individual%20from%20a%20different%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20Section%2098(1)%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Revenue%20Code%202006%20does%20not%20allow%20a%20landowner%20belonging%20to%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20to%20sell%2Fgift%2Fmortgage%2Flease%20any%20land%20to%20a%20person%20not%20belonging%20to%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%2C%20except%20with%20the%20previous%20permission%20of%20the%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarrating%20the%20woes%20that%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20family%20because%20of%20the%20year-long-pending%20case%2C%20Laxmi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20married%20off%20our%20daughter%20and%20have%20also%20been%20bearing%20medical%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20a%20month.%20To%20manage%20these%20expenses%2C%20we%20took%20loans%20worth%20Rs%205%20lakh.%20To%20repay%20the%20loan%20amounts%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20sell%20the%20land.%20So%20we%20brought%20our%20case%20to%20the%20collectorate%E2%80%99s%20notice%20but%20nobody%20listened%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20January%2C%20her%20case%20was%20resolved.%20%E2%80%9CThanks%20to%20the%20present%20DM%20%3Cem%3Esahab%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eour%20case%20got%20finalised%20in%20the%20second%20hearing%2C%20and%20we%20got%20the%20permission%20to%20sell%20our%20land.%20There%20were%20people%20in%20our%20village%20whose%20cases%20were%20pending%20for%20as%20long%20as%20five%20years%3B%20their%20cases%20were%20resolved%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20farmer%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Basti%20district%E2%80%99s%20Palha%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%