ent%20by%20100%20percent%20green%20electricity%20will%20only%20result%20in%2020%20percent%20decarbonisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20most%20of%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20Amit%20launched%20Hygenco%20in%202020%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20help%20India%20achieve%20energy%20independence%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20climate%20challenges%20continue%20to%20rise%2C%20and%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hygenco%20Green%20Energies%20signed%20a%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20green%20oxygen%20long-term%20offtake%20agreement%20with%20Sterlite%20Technologies%20Limited.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341877%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHygenco%20Green%20Energies%20signed%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20green%20oxygen%20long-term%20offtake%20agreement%20with%20Sterlite%20Technologies%20Limited.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20step%20closer%20towards%20green%20solutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20continues%20to%20inform%20that%20Hygen