20parent.%20When%20I%20looked%20around%20and%20saw%20the%20lack%20of%20infrastructure%20for%20pets%20in%20India%2C%20it%20made%20me%20wonder%20why%20in%20such%20a%20large%20country%20with%20a%20significant%20pet%20population%20we%20cannot%20have%20a%20facility%20that%20can%20save%20lives%20and%20make%20pet%20lives%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F266997%2Fjrd-tata-viral-letter-chairman-ratan-tata-group-net-worth-history-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERatan%20Tata%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Tata%20Trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20firsthand%20the%20services%20and%20care%20provided%20at%20a%20world-class%20veterinary%20hospital%2C%20he%20returned%20with%20a%20wish%20to%20build%20a%20similar%20one%20in%20Mumbai.%20His%20vision%20is%20finally%20materialising%2C%20many%20decades%20later.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Small%20Animal%20Hospital%20aims%20to%20be%20one%20such%20facility%20with%20specialised%20facilities%20to%20treat%20every%20pet%20with%20care%2C%20love%20and%20a%20human%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20The%20hospital%20will%20be%20led%20by%20Dr%20Thomas%20Heathcote%2C%20a%20British%20veterinarian%20with%20a%20vision%20of%20enhancing%20the%20quality%20of%20pet%20healthcare%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20pet%20is%20no%20different%20from%20a%20member%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20family%20today.%20As%20the%20guardian%20of%20several%20pets%20throughout%20my%20life%2C%20I%20recognise%20the%20need%20for%20this%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708005033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341951%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Trust%E2%80%99s%20Small%20Animal%20Hospital%20will%20be%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%2024*7%20hospitals%20for%20furry%20fr