20through%20%E2%80%98Share%20At%20Door%20Step%E2%80%99%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341516%2Fchennai-startup-global-green-coir-anees-ahmed-turns-coconut-husk-into-cocopeat-grow-bags%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20it%20easy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20me.%20In%20the%20time%20that%20I%20would%20spend%20hand-washing%20the%20clothes%2C%20I%20now%20tell%20stories%20to%20my%20grandkids%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20heartwarming%20tales%20highlight%20the%20core%20purpose%20that%20drives%20charitable%20donations%2C%20an%20intent%20to%20let%20someone%20experience%20the%20same%20joy%20you%20once%20did%20with%20an%20object%20of%20clothing%20or%20a%20toy.%20This%20is%20the%20foundational%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%98Share%20At%20Door%20Step%E2%80%99%20created%20by%20Anushka%20Jain%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20computer%20science%20engineer%20who%20is%20now%20in%20her%20thirties%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98sharing%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20birthday%2C%20Anushka%20would%20ask%20her%20mother%20which%20NGO%20they%20would%20be%20visiting%20that%20year.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20one%20each%20time%2C%20you%20see.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mum%20would%20pick%20an%20NGO%20in%20the%20city%20and%20we%E2%80%99d%20take%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330673%2Fgi-tagged-mithai-sweets-of-india-dharwad-peda-bebinca-khaje-moa-mihidana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweets%20and%20snacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20a%20great%20time%20with%20the%20kids%20and%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20should%20the%20fun%20be%20limited%20to%20just%20one%20day%20in%20the%20year%2C%20thought%20Anushka.%20She%20wanted%20%E2%80%98sharing%E2%80%99%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20her%20routine.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20college%20that%20a%20deeper%20delve%20into%20this%20question%20led%20Anushka%20to%20the%20answers.%20People%20didn%E2%80%99t%20shy%20away%20from%20donations%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20time.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20the%20ordeal%20of%20navigating%20the%20thicket%20of%20NGOs%20that%20kept%20them%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20tough%20to%20figure%20out%20which%20NGO%20your%20donation%20will%20benefit%20the%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20agrees%20Anushka%20who%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20in%202012%20with%20a%20dream%20to%20solve%20this%20dilemma%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340982%2Fiit-delhi-graduates-aroleap-x-fitness-home-gym-smart-ai-strength-training-equipment-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehunger%20for%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20she%20joined%20her%20dream%20company%20Accenture%2C%20where%20she%20worked%20the%20night%20shift%2C%20her%20mornings%20were%20spent%20very%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20of%20donating%20to%20NGOs%20never%20left%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20created%20a%20website%2C%20asked%20people%20around%20the%20city%20to%20register%20the%20items%20they%20wanted%20to%20donate%20and%20went%20around%20in%20the%20mornings%20doing%20pickups!%E2%80%9D%20After%20hitting%20200%20pickups%2C%20it%20dawned%20on%20Anushka%20that%20the%20idea%20was%20getting%20traction.%20She%20needed%20hands%20on%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG-20240215-WA0020-1707998597.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20donations%20at%20Share%20At%20Door%20Step%20include%20household%20items%20like%20washing%20machines%2C%20furniture%2C%20decor%2C%20toys%2C%20clothes%2C%20shoes%2C%20etc%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup