uccess%20rate.%20Whenever%20the%20topic%20of%20love%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20silver%20years%20is%20addressed%2C%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20think%20back%20to%20the%20year%202015.%20If%20you%20recall%2C%20there%20was%20a%20story%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338685%2Fsenior-citizen-woman-paragliding-paramotoring-viral-video-on-x-twitter-adventure-sports-usha-thuse-anand-mahindra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20couple%20in%20their%20sixties%3C%2Fa%3E%20finding%20love.%20It%20broke%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannels%20and%20digital%20publications%20cited%20the%20story%20as%20proof%20of%20the%20shift%20in%20the%20way%20relationships%20were%20perceived%20in%20India%20and%20the%20acceptance%20of%20more%20modern%20ideologies.%20But%2C%20while%20we%20may%20like%20to%20think%20that%20live-in%20relationships%20have%20gotten%20their%20blessing%20from%20society%2C%20it%20is%20still%20taboo%20in%20many%20places%20and%20an%20unspoken%20sacrilege%20in%20rural%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20Anil%20Yardi%20and%20Asawari%20Kulkarni%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdating%20in%20old%20age%E2%80%9D%20story%20emerged%2C%20the%20world%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20conversation%20starter%20to%20how%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336383%2Fhomemade-hyderabadi-biryani-in-bengaluru-by-noons-biryani-couple-entrepreneurs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20beginning%20to%20shed%20their%20inhibitions%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20couple%20completes%20nine%20years%20of%20togetherness%2C%20they%20look%20back%20on%20the%20epic%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKulkarni%20who%20retired%20in%202012%20had%20been%20alone%20since%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20demise%20in%201997.%20Work%20occupied%20her%20mind%20but%20it%20was%20